  ('MoBlack Records', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demo@moblack.com', '{"afro-house","deep-house","melodic-house-&-tech","tribal"}', null, null, 'Send private SoundCloud links only. No file attachments Confirmed on labelsbase.net and moblack.com/auto-draft contact page. Also promo@moblack.com for promos.', '{"moblack.com/auto-draft","labelsbase.net/moblack-records","beatstats.com/label/moblack-records/37162-genre89"}', 'Consistently #1–2 top-selling label in Beatport''s Afro House genre. Founded 2013 by Italian-Ghanaian producer MoBlack, it is the defining imprint of modern afro house globally, with hundreds of releases and a verified open demo email. High streaming credibility, strong booking impact, and openly accessible to unknowns.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Stay True Sounds', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/staytruesounds/portal', '{"afro-house","deep-house","soulful-house"}', null, null, 'Use private SoundCloud links for email route. LabelRadar portal for streamlined submission LabelRadar portal confirmed active (TikTok announcement + Defected/LabelRadar partnership news 2023). Email confirmed on labelsbase.net. Both routes open.', '{"labelradar.com/labels/staytruesounds/portal","labelsbase.net/stay-true-sounds","musicweek.com/labels/read/defected-opens-up-demo-submissions-through-beatport-music-services-division-s-labelradar-programme/088481"}', 'South African deep/afro house label co-founded by Kid Fonque and Jullian Gomes; acquired by Defected Records. Has LabelRadar portal AND an email route, both publicly accessible. Defected partnership gives global streaming and retail reach. Accessible to unknown artists through both channels.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Sondela Recordings', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@sondelarecordings.com', '{"afro-house","afro-electronic","deep-house"}', null, null, 'Demo email confirmed directly in footer of sondelarecordings.com. Also info@sondelarecordings.com for general queries.', '{"sondelarecordings.com","essentialhouse.club/2025/08/va-sondela-sampler-vol-4-on-sondela-recordings-ltd","defected.com/news/post/defected-launch-afro-house-label-sondela"}', 'Defected''s dedicated afro house imprint, launched 2021. Active Boiler Room partnerships, continuous 2024–2026 releases (Sondela Sampler series). Strong global streaming reach under Defected umbrella. Dedicated demo email confirmed on their own website.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Madorasindahouse', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demo@madorasindahouse.com', '{"afro-house","deep-house","afro-electronic"}', null, null, 'Confirmed at madorasindahouse.com/contact. Additional A&R contacts: harrys@madorasindahouse.com, alkis@madorasindahouse.com.', '{"madorasindahouse.com/contact","ra.co/labels/19308","beatportal.com/labels/686676-madorasindahouse"}', 'Greece''s leading afro house label and party brand; 10+ years running events across Europe and Africa. Strong Beatportal presence. Dedicated demo emails confirmed on their own contact page. Scene respect high in European afro house circuit, accessible to unknown artists.', '2026-06-01'),

