  ('LouLou Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'kolombo@loulourecords.com', '{"tech-house","latin-tech-house","jackin-house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only A&R email confirmed on labelsbase.net as kolombo@loulourecords.com. General contact also at info@loulourecords.com.', '{"labelsbase.net/loulou-records","essentialhouse.club/2025/06/va-loulou-records-summer-sampler-2025-on-loulou-records","beatport.com/label/loulou-records/9364"}', 'Belgian label founded by LouLou Players with strong Latin/Brazilian tech house flavor. 116 tech house releases on Beatport, active 2024–2025 (Summer Sampler 2025, Best Of 2024/2025 compilations). Accessible via email with SoundCloud link. Kolombo handles A&R; label friendly to new talent.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Tribe Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'info@triberecordsuk.com', '{"afro-house","deep-house","soulful-house"}', null, null, 'info@triberecordsuk.com is listed on the official triberecordsuk.com contact page as the general enquiries address; no dedicated demo email published. Label is active with releases through 2025.', '{"triberecordsuk.com/gallery","beatport.com/label/tribe-records/12923/releases"}', 'Boutique London label founded by Zepherin Saint — a key figure in afro house history. 37 Beatport afro house releases, active 2024–2025 (confirmed via Beatport year range). Soul, afro and jazz at its core. General enquiries email confirmed on their own website. Accessible to unknown artists.', '2026-06-01'),

