  ('Watergate Records', 'a', 'needs_warm_intro', 'email', 'label@water-gate.de', '{"deep-house","afro-house","melodic-house-&-techno"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only. High production quality expected Email confirmed on labelsbase.net. Label is prestigious — unknown artists without existing profile should expect low response rate. A warm introduction via an artist already on the label significantly improves chances.', '{"labelsbase.net/watergate-records","water-gate.de/de/label/label.html","ufo-network.com/2024/10/08/fahlberg-rhythms-for-sale-ep"}', 'Berlin club-label with elite reputation; 25 afro house releases on Beatport, active in 2024–2025. Releases afro house alongside melodic/deep house and techno. Demonstrated demo email published on labelsbase.net; however, given its prestige (Berlin club imprint), unknown artists face a high quality bar. Warm intro strongly advised, though email is technically public.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Vatos Locos', 'b', 'needs_warm_intro', 'dm', null, '{"tech-house","afro-tech","latin-tech-house"}', null, null, 'No public demo email or form found. Best approach is Instagram DM (@vatos.locos.official) or SoundCloud. labelsbase.net had no page for this label. Confidence low — unverified channel.', '{"soundcloud.com/vatos-locos-official","instagram.com/vatos.locos.official","djmag.com/news/hector-launches-new-vatos-locos-label"}', 'Barcelona-based label by DJ Hector with strong Latin/afro-inflected tech house releases on Beatport. Scene respect is high in the tech house circuit. No publicly confirmed demo email found — social channels (Instagram @vatos.locos.official, SoundCloud) are the only accessible contact points. Likely needs a warm introduction or direct DM with strong music.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Hood Politics Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@hoodpoliticsrecords.com', '{"bass-house","tech-house","house"}', null, null, 'Official site links to tstack.app/hoodpoliticsrecords for submissions. Email is listed as alternative channel on labelsbase.net. Label states A&R team is relentlessly active.', '{"hoodpoliticsrecords.com","labelsbase.net/hoodpoliticsrecords","beatport.com/label/hood-politics-records/65821"}', 'San Diego–based collective (also described as Chicago-rooted) with strong Beatport presence across bass house, tech house and house. Actively releasing in 2024 (e.g. ''Pretty Boy Swag'' by Proppa, Dec 2024; ''Six Five Four'' by Shifty, Sept 2024). Known for community-driven curation and open to unknown artists via a stated always-on A&R policy. Scenes respect + streaming credibility well established.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('House of Hustle', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@houseofhustle.co', '{"tech-house","bass-house","house"}', null, null, 'private SoundCloud links only Listed on LabelRadar (labelradar.com/labels/HouseOfHustleLabel/profile). Email sourced from labelsbase.net.', '{"labelsbase.net/house-of-hustle","labelradar.com/labels/HouseOfHustleLabel/profile","beatport.com/label/house-of-hustle/42127"}', 'Boutique dance label founded 2014 with a strong Beatport catalog (640+ tech house tracks, 59+ bass house). Dedicated ''attitude'' aesthetic across big basslines, 808s and party-focused club music. Active on Beatport through 2024-2025. Listed on LabelRadar, confirming they actively use the platform to manage demo intake. Well-suited to an unknown artist with polished tech/bass house material.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Dim Mak Records', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@dimmak.com', '{"bass-house","tech-house","house","electro-house"}', null, null, 'private SoundCloud links only Official demos page at dimmak.com/demos confirmed; also on LabelRadar (labelradar.com/labels/dimmak/profile). Email and SoundCloud-link requirement confirmed via labelsbase.net.', '{"dimmak.com/demos","labelsbase.net/dim-mak-records","labelradar.com/labels/dimmak/profile"}', 'Independent LA label founded by Steve Aoki in 1996. Has a dedicated /demos page and official email; maintains LabelRadar portal. Active 2024-2025 across bass house and tech house (e.g., Rich DietZ ''House Music & Anime'' 2025). Known for ''New Noise'' imprint discovering emerging talent. Beatport presence is strong and genre scope includes house and bass-adjacent. Accessible to unknown artists per their own stated ''by any means necessary'' ethos.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Bunny Tiger', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'info@bunnytiger.de', '{"tech-house","bass-house","house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only Confirmed via labelsbase which cites official Instagram as source.', '{"labelsbase.net/bunny-tiger","instagram.com/bunnytigerofficial"}', 'Founded 2012 by Sharam Jey with a ''DJ tools for DJs'' philosophy. Active through 2024-2025 on Beatport (91+ tech house, 8+ bass house releases). Consistent label with scene respect and a roster of international underground talent. Beatport, Traxsource and RA profiles all active. Contact email is public and the requirement for private SoundCloud links indicates they actively manage demo intake.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('REALM Records', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@realm-records.com', '{"house","tech-house","melodic-house","afro-house","deep-house"}', null, null, 'Email confirmed via Gorgon City Facebook post (realmrecordsdemos@gmail.com also referenced in 2021 post). Primary demo email demos@realm-records.com and tstack URL from findmylabels.com. Also on LabelRadar (labelradar.com/labels/therealm/portal).', '{"facebook.com/gorgoncity/posts/where-to-send-demos-for-our-label-realm-realmrecordsdemosgmailcom/1832679666793412","findmylabels.com/realm-records","labelradar.com/labels/therealm/portal","beatport.com/label/realm-records/74459"}', 'Founded 2018 by Gorgon City. Active and growing in 2024-2025 (album ''Reverie'' via REALM & Astralwerks 2024; Beatport imprint presence confirmed via ADE 2024 chart). Strong streaming credibility and scene respect (Gorgon City are booking-relevant headline acts). Accepts demos via public email and tstack portal per confirmed official channels. Genres include house and tech house which crossover well with US-leaning bass house producers.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('IN/ROTATION (Insomniac Records)', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/insomniac/portal', '{"tech-house","house","bass-house","deep-house"}', null, null, 'Submit via the Insomniac Records LabelRadar portal; covers IN/ROTATION and other Insomniac imprints. Genres accepted: Deep House, Tech House, House, Melodic Techno, Progressive House, Techno per findmylabels.com.', '{"labelradar.com/labels/insomniac/portal","findmylabels.com/insomniac-records","insomniacmusicgroup.com/label/in-rotation","beatport.com/label/in-rotation-insomniac-records/64140"}', 'Insomniac''s dedicated house/tech-house imprint since 2017. ''Rotate'' compilation series runs into Vol. 15+ (2025), demonstrating sustained commissioning activity. Parent company Insomniac runs major US festivals (EDC, HARD) — label exposure translates directly to booking visibility. LabelRadar portal is the confirmed submission channel (labelradar.com/labels/insomniac/portal), one of the strongest cold-submit platforms in the industry. Actively accepting house, tech house, deep house, melodic techno.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Stress Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@stress-records.com', '{"house","tech-house","nu-disco","deep-house"}', null, null, 'Demo email confirmed directly on the official stress-records.com/contact/ page. Discord community at discord.com/invite/sErhkswXbR. Label is active with releases through April 2026.', '{"stress-records.com/contact","stressrecords.bandcamp.com","beatport.com/label/stress-records/73655"}', 'Long-running UK-based house label run by Needwant Limited (also behind Future Disco). Very active through 2025-2026 (multiple Club Culture volumes; April 2026 releases confirmed on Bandcamp). Beatport and Beatsource presence strong. Known for artists like Ben Hemsley, Friend Within, Emily Nash. Has a Discord community for fans and the demo email is publicly listed on the official contact page — good accessibility signal.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Sleazy Deep', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'rob@sleazydeep.com', '{"deep-house","house","nu-disco","tech-house"}', null, null, 'Email sourced from SoundCloud profile bio and secondary source confirmation. Label also operates Sleazy G sub-imprint for G-house. Rob Made Linktree at linktr.ee/robmade.', '{"sleazydeep.com","sleazydeep.bandcamp.com/album/everything-changes-ep","ra.co/labels/7080"}', 'London-based collective founded 2011 by Rob Made. Nu skool disco, deep house funk and ultra-modern sonics — crossover appeal for US bass/house producers. Confirmed active in 2024: ''Everything Changes EP'' released May 10 2024; ''CLUBTRAXX Vol 1'' released April 12 2024 (both confirmed on Bandcamp). Beatport chart positions and Mixmag support documented. Sub-label Sleazy G features G-house artists including Amine Edge & DANCE and Shiba San, directly relevant to the bass-house crossover target.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Late Checkout Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@latecheckout.info', '{"bass-house","house","uk-bass","garage"}', null, null, 'Official demos page (latecheckout.info/demos) returned connection refused; email corroborated by multiple secondary sources', '{"latecheckout.info/releases","labelsbase.net/late-checkout-records"}', 'Founded 2022 by Chris Lorenzo (UK) with a clear bass house and garage-influenced identity. Active through Dec 2024: ''U Should Not Be Doing That'' with Amyl & The Sniffers (Dec 2024), ''Pump'' AC Slater Remix (Jul 2024). Strong Beatport presence in bass house genre. Has a dedicated /demos page (latecheckout.info/demos) that was indexed, indicating active intake. Direct crossover with US bass house scene via AC Slater collaboration; accessible to unknown artists.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Glitterbox Recordings', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/glitterbox/portal', '{"soulful-house","disco-house","nu-disco","vocal-house"}', null, null, 'Submit via LabelRadar portal. Genre: soulful house, disco-influenced house, vocal house Part of the Defected LabelRadar family launched Sep 2023. Portal confirmed active. Acceptance rate ~3-5%.', '{"labelradar.com/labels/glitterbox/portal","beatportal.com/articles/155155-defected-records-is-now-open-for-demo-submissions-via-labelradar","defected.com/glitterbox"}', 'Defected''s premium soulful-house and disco sub-label; Purple Disco Machine, Mousse T., Folamour, The Shapeshifters. Officially opened submissions via LabelRadar in 2023 — the first time Defected/Glitterbox accepted cold demos. Strong Beatport, Traxsource and streaming credibility; major booking impact; scene royalty.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Classic Music Company', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/classicmusiccompany/portal', '{"deep-house","classic-house","soulful-house","disco"}', null, null, 'Submit via LabelRadar portal. Classic / deep / soulful house only LabelRadar portal confirmed in search results. Part of Defected LabelRadar umbrella.', '{"labelradar.com/labels/classicmusiccompany/portal","ra.co/labels/17215","beatportal.com/articles/155155-defected-records-is-now-open-for-demo-submissions-via-labelradar"}', 'Set up in 1994 by Derrick Carter and Luke Solomon — the originators of classic Chicago house — now operating as a Defected-distributed imprint. Honey Dijon, Eli Escobar, Red Rack''em, Juan Maclean. Elite scene respect, strong Beatport and booking pull, now fully open via LabelRadar.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Freerange Records', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'info@freerangerecords.co.uk', '{"deep-house","soulful-house","house"}', null, null, 'Email with private SoundCloud link. Deep / soulful house focus Confirmed on official site freerangerecords.co.uk as the only public contact address. No dedicated demos@ address; info@ is listed for general enquiries and serves as the demo contact.', '{"freerangerecords.co.uk","labelsbase.net/freerange-records"}', 'London-based deep house institution since 1997 — 28 years, 300+ EPs. Home to Jimpster, Detroit Swindle, Milton Jackson, Lovebirds, Manuel Tur. Beatport and Traxsource chart regular. Active as of June 2025 with new Jimpster/OVEOUS release. Premier scene credibility; genuinely reachable for unknown artists via email.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Delusions of Grandeur', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'hi@delusionsofgrandeur.com', '{"deep-house","soulful-house","disco"}', null, null, 'Email via general contact. Deep, underground house and disco only hi@delusionsofgrandeur.com is the general enquiries address on the official site; no separate dedicated demo email found.', '{"delusionsofgrandeur.com","ra.co/labels/2975"}', 'London''s premier deep-house-and-disco boutique label since 2009. Tom Roberts and Jimpster curate with extreme care; Session Victim, Gerd, Levantine. Active through 2025 (Constellation EP Jan 2025). Beatport and Traxsource presence. Warm reputation for breaking unknown artists that fit the sound.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Local Talk', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'dm', 'https://localtalk.bandcamp.com/', '{"deep-house","classic-house","soulful-house"}', null, null, 'Use Bandcamp contact form or reach out via social channels. Classic / soulful deep house No public demo email or official submission page found for Local Talk. The Bandcamp page has a generic ''Contact Local Talk'' form. The label''s own site (thelocaltalk.se) did not surface submission details. The claimed dm method cannot be confirmed against an official source.', '{"localtalk.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/6275"}', 'Stockholm-based deep-house label run by Mad Mats and Tooli since 2009; lauded for bringing Scandinavian deep house to global dancefloors. Active on Beatport and Traxsource with 2024-2025 releases. Both founders personally listen to every demo. Scene respect among deep house purists.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Dirt Crew Recordings', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demo@dirtcrew.net', '{"deep-house","house","electronica"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only. Allow 2-3 weeks for response. Every demo is listened to Demo email confirmed via official contact page (dirtcrew.net redirects to Bandcamp) and multiple secondary sources. Selection 2024 released Dec 13 2024 confirms active status.', '{"dirtcrew.net/pages/contact","dirtcrew.bandcamp.com/album/selection-2024","labelsbase.net/dirt-crew-recordings"}', 'Berlin-based deep-house label since 2004, 200+ releases. Selection 2024 compilation released Dec 2024 — definitively active. Beatport and Traxsource listed. Known for working with unknown artists across genres. Published demo email and turnaround promise publicly on their website.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Z Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'gordon@zrecords.ltd.uk', '{"deep-house","soulful-house","disco","nu-disco"}', null, null, 'Send links — NOT MP3s. Email gordon@zrecords.ltd.uk Demo contact confirmed directly on the official Z Records website contact page. Gordon is the label manager. Dave Lee''s own label so highly curated — quality bar is high.', '{"zrecords.ltd.uk/contact","labelsbase.net/z-records-4894","demolist.app/table-1-details/z-records-demo-submission/r/rec75yoLs4XKpzi4U"}', 'Founded 1990 by Dave Lee (Joey Negro); one of the longest-running UK soul/house labels. Z Records sits at the intersection of deep house, nu-disco and soulful house — perfectly aligned. Beatport presence, regular DJ chart appearances. Open to unknown artists; demo email published publicly.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Razor-N-Tape', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'tapey@razor-n-tape.com', '{"deep-house","disco","nu-disco","classic-house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only Labelsbase lists tapey@razor-n-tape.com as the A&R demo email. The alternative demos@razor-n-tape.com is mentioned in secondary sources but labelsbase cites tapey@ as the primary contact. Claimed email matches.', '{"labelsbase.net/razor-n-tape-records","ra.co/labels/8037"}', 'Brooklyn-born disco and deep house label since 2012. Known for original house, disco edits and compilations. Family Affair Vol. 4 dropped Dec 2024 — definitively active. 100+ releases, Beatport and Traxsource presence. Known to bring in fresh talent; accessible demo contact.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Shall Not Fade', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScnxR3qcD4b-T2Om0iE0E124hLZYc1a_B51IM37OZUDHlvK9A/viewform', '{"deep-house","house","soulful-house","uk-house"}', null, null, 'Artist name. Instagram handle. Previous label history. Private SoundCloud playlist link (as many tracks as possible). Email address. Additional info / planned releases Form confirmed active and accepting responses as of June 2026 via direct fetch. Titled ''DEMO SUBMISSION FORM 2023'' but still live. Linked from official Linktree (linktr.ee/shallnotfade). Also covers sister labels Time Is Now and Lost Palms.', '{"linktr.ee/shallnotfade","docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScnxR3qcD4b-T2Om0iE0E124hLZYc1a_B51IM37OZUDHlvK9A/viewform","ra.co/labels/12884"}', 'Bristol-based label launched Dec 2015. Active release schedule on Beatport and Traxsource. Runs a dedicated Google Form for demo submissions — one of the most open, artist-friendly submission systems for underground house. Covers SNF, Time Is Now, Lost Palms sub-labels. Scene respect among UK house community.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Wolf Music Recordings', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'mattwolfmusic@gmail.com', '{"deep-house","soulful-house","disco"}', null, null, 'Email Matt Neale directly No dedicated demo@ address found. mattwolfmusic@gmail.com is the licensing/general contact for Matt Neale (label co-founder); this is the best public contact for demos. Contact page at wolfmusicrecords.com/contact inaccessible. Confidence low — demo channel unconfirmed from a primary source.', '{"wolfmusicrecords.com","juno.co.uk/junodaily/2026/02/09/tom-esselle-on-second-wolf-music-outing-its-a-vocal-sample-i-knew-i-wanted-to-give-the-deep-house-treatment","beatportal.com/articles/1047993-hype-label-of-the-month-wolf-music-recordings"}', 'UK-based independent deep house and disco label since 2009. Active through 2025-2026 (Tom Esselle EP Feb 2026, Beatportal Hype Label of the Month). Frits Wentink, Retromigration, Harold Heath. Genuine underground credibility; Beatport and Traxsource presence. One of the most respected UK deep house boutique labels.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Toy Tonics', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'info@toytonics.de', '{"deep-house","disco","nu-disco","italo-house","indie-dance"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only info@toytonics.de serves as both general contact and demo A&R email per labelsbase.net; label active with May 2026 release', '{"labelsbase.net/toy-tonics","toytonics.de/releases"}', 'Berlin-based independent label and culture crew since 2012. Monthly EPs on vinyl and digital. Releases Kapote, Alma Negra, Harvey Sutherland remixes. Italomania Vol. 3 (2024) and consistent 2025 releases confirm active status. Beatport, Traxsource, Kompakt distribution. Known for eclectic, funky, disco-influenced house.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Permanent Vacation', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'info@perm-vac.com', '{"disco","nu-disco","balearic","cosmic-house","deep-house"}', null, null, 'Label cannot return unsolicited material unless stamped addressed envelope included. Do not send physical material without return envelope info@perm-vac.com confirmed directly on official website about page. Label explicitly states they accept unsolicited material submissions.', '{"perm-vac.com/about","labelsbase.net/permanent-vacation","perm-vac.bandcamp.com/album/permanent-vacation-selected-label-works-12"}', 'Munich/Berlin label since 2006 run by Tom Bioly and Benjamin Fröhlich. Premier European disco and cosmic house imprint. Selected Label Works 12 released Dec 2025, confirming current activity. Strong Beatport, Traxsource, and streaming presence. Respected across the Balearic/disco/deep spectrum; open to unsolicited demos.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Soul Clap Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'records@soulclap.us', '{"deep-house","soulful-house","funk","r&b-house"}', null, null, 'Email to records@soulclap.us Active label; released House of EFUNK 2025 compilation (July 2025). records@soulclap.us confirmed by multiple secondary sources as the demo contact.', '{"soulclaprecords.bandcamp.com","soundcloud.com/soulclaprecs","ra.co/labels/8534"}', 'Boston-based label founded on deep house and soul. Soul Clap Records was started specifically because they were receiving outstanding demos — demos drive the label. Active in 2024-2025 (Amazement Aug 2024, EcoSystemS Mar 2024). Beatport and Traxsource presence. Famous duo run it personally.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Aus Music', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'info@ausmusic.co.uk', '{"deep-house","melodic-house","leftfield-house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only Official site ausmusic.co.uk currently returning fatal PHP error but email info@ausmusic.co.uk confirmed via labelsbase.net and Instagram profile. Label is active (© 2026 Aus Music / Simple Records Ltd on site).', '{"ausmusic.co.uk","labelsbase.net/aus-music","ra.co/labels/796"}', 'London label founded 2006 by Will Saul (Simple Records) and Fink. Celebrated 200th release in 2024 with celebratory EP series; Sunchaser released Feb 2026 — definitively active. Beatport top-selling deep house. ''Label of the Month'' April 2025 on Beatportal. Releases club-ready music with cultured edge. Genuinely listens to demos.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('King Street Sounds', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'rich@kingstreetsounds.com', '{"soulful-house","deep-house","vocal-house","classic-house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only. Soulful/deep house focus labelsbase lists rich@kingstreetsounds.com as A&R demo contact. Old Facebook post referenced trax4kss@gmail.com (stale). Official contact page returned 403. Claimed email matches labelsbase.', '{"labelsbase.net/king-street-sounds","kingstreetsounds.com"}', 'Founded 1993 at the Paradise Garage era in NYC; one of the oldest and most respected independent house labels. Under Armada Music partnership since 2024. House Music Royalty documentary Dec 2024. Dennis Ferrer, David Morales, Ultra Naté alumni. Beatport, Traxsource, Armada distribution. Premium scene legitimacy. Sub-labels Nite Grooves and Street King also reach.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Skylax Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'contact@skylaxrecords.com', '{"deep-house","house","classic-house"}', null, null, 'Use contact form at skylaxrecords.com/en/nous-contacter. Or email contact@skylaxrecords.com contact@skylaxrecords.com confirmed on official website and labelsbase.net. Contact form available with file upload. Label accepts demos for consideration.', '{"skylaxrecords.com/en/nous-contacter","labelsbase.net/skylax-records","skylaxrecords.bandcamp.com/album/skylax-records-mega-bundles-bandcamp-exclusive"}', 'French label since 2004 run by Hardrock Striker; mission to release timeless music that stands apart. Skylax Mega Bundle Dec 2024 confirms active. Beatport and Traxsource listed. Bridge.audio submission directory active. Nurtures emerging artists alongside seasoned DJs. Underground European house credibility.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Heist Recordings', 'b', 'needs_warm_intro', null, 'https://heistrecordings.myshopify.com/pages/contact', '{"deep-house","soulful-house","underground-house"}', null, null, 'Use general contact form on website. No dedicated demo email confirmed No public demo email found across official website, Bandcamp, Linktree, or any aggregator. Contact form available at heistrecordings.myshopify.com/pages/contact (general inquiries). Label documented as receiving too many demos to manage. Cold approach not recommended without a referral.', '{"heistrecordings.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/9847","909originals.com/2024/08/04/dam-swindle-release-compilation-of-heist-recordings-biggest-anthems"}', 'Amsterdam label founded by Dam Swindle — champions of underground house, Cinthie, DJ Sneak, Byron the Aquarius, Crackazat. Compilation of biggest anthems released Aug 2024 confirms active. Beatport and Traxsource presence. Strong scene respect and booking pull. However, known to receive far more demos than they can handle.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Nurvous Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'andrew@nervousnyc.com', '{"nu-disco","indie-dance","disco","deep-house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only. Indie dance / nu-disco focus for Nurvous specifically Nurvous is a sub-label of Nervous Records launched in 2011. Official nervousnyc.com/about/ lists Andrew@nervousnyc.com for A&R & Licensing and the Trackstack portal. Claimed email andrew@nervousnyc.com is confirmed correct.', '{"nervousnyc.com/about","labelsbase.net/nurvous-records"}', 'NYC sub-label of Nervous Records since 2011; focuses on indie dance and nu-disco — sits squarely in the disco/deep house crossover zone. 1518+ Beatport releases; active through 2024-2025 per Beatport catalog. Accessible via the Nervous Records A&R contact. Accessible to unknown artists in the indie dance/nu-disco space.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('D4 D4NCE', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/d4d4nce/portal', '{"deep-house","soulful-house","underground-house"}', null, null, 'Submit via LabelRadar portal. Underground house focus LabelRadar portal confirmed active per search results; part of Defected''s LabelRadar partnership launched Sep 2023. Same portal system as Glitterbox and Classic Music Company.', '{"labelradar.com/labels/d4d4nce/portal","beatportal.com/articles/155155-defected-records-is-now-open-for-demo-submissions-via-labelradar","edmhousenetwork.com/iconic-house-music-label-defected-records-partners-with-labelradar-to-discover-new-talent"}', 'Defected sub-label focused on underground house with commercial appeal. Part of the same Defected LabelRadar ecosystem as Glitterbox and Classic Music Company — one submission potentially reaching multiple Defected imprints. Active releases on Beatport. Good entry point for deep house artists targeting the Defected ecosystem without competing directly with the main imprint.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Spinnin'' Records', 'elite', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://spinninrecords.com/talentpool/', '{"house","tech-house","progressive-house","big-room","future-house"}', null, null, 'Original tracks only, no remixes/bootlegs. Submit via Talent Pool platform or email with private SoundCloud link. One track per week limit on Talent Pool. Must be 18+ or have parental consent. 3-month exclusivity window Also accepts submissions via LabelRadar at labelradar.com/labels/spinninrecords/portal. Talent Pool contact: talentpool@spinninrecords.nl', '{"labelsbase.net/spinnin-records","spinninrecords.com/talentpool","labelradar.com/labels/spinninrecords/portal"}', 'World''s leading dance label with massive Beatport chart presence, global festival reach, and an open Talent Pool platform that actively signs unknown artists. Active tech-house and house releases in 2025. 3-month review window, weekly A&R feedback.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Spinnin'' Deep', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://spinninrecords.com/talentpool/', '{"house","tech-house","deep-house","future-house"}', null, null, 'Submit via Talent Pool portal or email with private SoundCloud link. Tech House, House, Deep House accepted Shared submission pipeline with Spinnin'' Records Talent Pool. Note ''Spinnin Deep'' in subject line or intro.', '{"labelsbase.net/spinnin-deep","findmylabels.com/spinnin-deep","spinninrecords.com/talentpool"}', 'House/tech-house sublabel of the world''s biggest dance label. Active with tech-house releases in 2025 (e.g., Joshwa ''Say My Name''). Shares the Talent Pool submission pipeline — slightly less competitive than main Spinnin'' Records for underground-leaning house.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Insomniac Records', 'elite', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/insomniac/portal', '{"house","tech-house","melodic-house","melodic-techno","progressive-house"}', null, null, 'Submit via LabelRadar portal. House, Tech House, Melodic Techno, Progressive House accepted Insomniac Music Group also has a ''demos'' contact tab at insomniacmusicgroup.com. LabelRadar is the primary confirmed route for Insomniac Records specifically.', '{"labelradar.com/labels/insomniac/portal","findmylabels.com/insomniac-records","insomniacmusicgroup.com/label/insomniac-records"}', 'Flagship label of Insomniac Music Group — the dominant US festival company (EDC, HARD). Strong Beatport chart presence, massive festival placement, direct career catalyst for unknown artists. Has active LabelRadar portal. Covers deep house, tech house, melodic across their group labels.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('STMPD RCRDS', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://demo.stmpdrcrds.com/', '{"house","tech-house","progressive-house","festival-house"}', null, null, 'Original tracks only — no remixes, no bootlegs. Must connect SoundCloud account to submit via portal. Submit once Email hello@martingarrix.com listed as secondary A&R contact by labelsbase.net — treat as medium-confidence. Primary verified route is demo.stmpdrcrds.com portal.', '{"demo.stmpdrcrds.com","labelsbase.net/stmpd-rcrds","festivalling.com/uncategorized/stmpd-rcrds-announces-demo-drop"}', 'Martin Garrix''s own imprint with massive streaming and festival reach. Has a dedicated public demo-drop portal. Active releases in 2025. Strong Tomorrowland and festival alignment. Career-launching for lesser-known acts.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Armada Music', 'elite', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://demodrop.armadamusic.com/', '{"house","tech-house","progressive-house","trance","melodic-house"}', null, null, 'Include artist background, achievements, track description, music style in under 10 sentences. Private SoundCloud link preferred. Also accepts via LabelRadar Armada University offers paid demo feedback service. ''Drop Your Demo'' button also appears on every page of armadamusic.com. Note label and sublabel (e.g., Armada Subjekt) in submission.', '{"demodrop.armadamusic.com","armadamusic.com/news/how-to-submit-your-demo","labelsbase.net/armada-music","labelradar.com/labels/armadamusic/profile"}', 'One of the world''s largest independent dance labels. Home to Armada Subjekt (house/tech-house), Armada Captivating, and more. Strong Beatport chart presence, streaming credibility, and open demo intake via DemoDrop platform.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Armada Subjekt', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demo@armadamusic.com', '{"house","tech-house"}', null, null, 'Email with subject line: ''Demo for Armada Subjekt''. Private SoundCloud link. Or submit via demodrop.armadamusic.com Shared submission pipeline with Armada Music parent label.', '{"labelsbase.net/armada-subjekt","armadamusic.com/labels/armada-subjekt","beatport.com/label/armada-subjekt/60906"}', 'Armada Music''s dedicated house and tech-house imprint. Active with 2025 releases (Miami, Ibiza compilations). Strong Beatport and streaming presence. Shares submission pipeline with Armada parent — directly accessible.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Musical Freedom', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@musicalfreedom.com', '{"house","bass-house","big-room","electro-house","future-house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud link only. Original tracks preferred Email confirmed by the label''s own official Twitter/X post (@musicalfreedom) stating ''Hey man, demos can go to demos@musicalfreedom.com''.', '{"twitter.com/musicalfreedom/status/172052520523403265","labelsbase.net/musical-freedom"}', 'Tiësto''s own imprint with strong streaming, festival and radio reach. Multiple recent releases. Publicly listed demo email confirmed via official Twitter post and secondary sources. Good discovery vehicle for crossover house acts.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('mau5trap', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/mau5trap/portal', '{"house","progressive-house","techno","electro-house","melodic-techno"}', null, null, 'Submit only one song at a time. Original work only. Progressive house, techno, electro house preferred Active open call for We Are Friends Vol. 12 compilation confirmed via Beatportal (Jan 2026). Email demos@mau5trap.com confirmed via findmylabels.com cross-check.', '{"beatportal.com/articles/963663-mau5trap-seeks-demos-we-are-friends-compilation-series","labelradar.com/labels/mau5trap/portal","findmylabels.com/mau5trap","edm.com/news/mau5trap-seeking-producer-submissions-new-we-are-friends-compilation"}', 'deadmau5''s imprint with decades of dance music credibility. Active LabelRadar portal confirmed. ''We Are Friends Vol. 12'' compilation launched 2026 as explicit open call for unknown artists — strong discovery track record (REZZ, Kasablanca, i_o). Active releases in 2025-2026.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Protocol Recordings', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://protocol-recordings.com/demo/', '{"house","progressive-house","electro-house","big-room"}', null, null, 'Exclusivity required — do not submit same demo to other labels simultaneously. No bootlegs, mash-ups, or promos. Submit via on-page widget or LabelRadar. Submit only once; allow up to 30 days for response After 30 days with no response, free to submit elsewhere. Nicky Romero also runs demo:drop at nickyromero.com/demodrop/. LabelRadar also accepted: labelradar.com/labels/protocolrecordings/profile', '{"protocol-recordings.com/demo","labelsbase.net/protocol-recordings","labelradar.com/labels/protocolrecordings/profile"}', 'Nicky Romero''s imprint with strong festival and streaming reach. Fully open demo submission page on official site, plus LabelRadar. Regularly gives public demo feedback on Twitch. Active releases in 2025.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('HEXAGON', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.hexagonhq.com/', '{"house","future-house","bass-house","electro-house"}', null, null, 'House, Bass House, Club Bangers preferred. Submit via Trackstack on hexagonhq.com. Don Diablo personally reviews submissions Demo submission uses Trackstack platform embedded on hexagonhq.com. Direct demo email demo@dondiablo.com confirmed via labelsbase.net and official HexagonHQ Twitter reply. Hexagonhq.com/demo returned 404; main site hexagonhq.com confirmed Trackstack demo section.', '{"hexagonhq.com","labelsbase.net/hexagon","x.com/hexagonhq/status/717464958544580609","edm.com/news/don-diablo-new-hexagon-era"}', 'Don Diablo''s own label celebrating 10 years in 2025. Strong Beatport chart presence, Hexagon Radio in 68+ countries, and Tomorrowland residency. Entered ''HEXAGON 2.0'' era 2025. Claims Don opens every demo personally. Active house/future-house releases.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Smash The House', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demo@smashthehouse.com', '{"house","big-room","electro-house","festival-house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only Generation Smash sublabel specifically targets emerging artists. Smash Deep focuses on deeper sounds.', '{"labelsbase.net/smash-the-house","1001tracklists.com/tracklist/26fn11d9/dimitri-vegas-like-mike-smash-the-house-radio-655-2025-12-19.html","beatport.com/label/smash-the-house-official/82378"}', 'Dimitri Vegas & Like Mike''s label with massive festival footprint (Tomorrowland headliners). Active releases in 2025. Weekly radio show with 655+ episodes. Has Generation Smash sublabel for emerging artists. Open demo email confirmed via labelsbase.net.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Monstercat Silk', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/monstercatsilk/portal', '{"house","progressive-house","deep-house","melodic-house","chillout"}', null, null, 'Submit original work only. Progressive House, Deep House, House, Chillout accepted General contact: support@monstercat.com. LabelRadar is the primary submission channel for Monstercat Silk.', '{"labelradar.com/labels/monstercatsilk/portal","labelsbase.net/monstercat-silk","monstercat.com/silk","beatport.com/label/silk-music/13068"}', 'Monstercat''s house and progressive imprint. Active 2025 releases (Silk Selections 06, Dec 2025). Fully open LabelRadar portal. Strong Spotify editorial and streaming presence. Acquired from Silk Music label, legitimate progressive house home for emerging producers.', '2026-06-01'),

