  ('Enormous Tunes', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeqFSQszOxYuOMwiP52kDo9QGJRz7UV50t_QIN8h2KM2QX-mw/viewform', '{"house","progressive-house","melodic-house"}', null, null, 'Submit via Google Form or LabelRadar. Private SoundCloud links when using email LabelRadar portal also available: labelradar.com/labels/enormoustunes/portal. Google Form confirmed on official Enormous Tunes contact page (enormoustunes.com/contact). Label focuses on house and progressive house.', '{"enormoustunes.com/contact","labelsbase.net/enormous-tunes","labelradar.com/labels/enormoustunes/portal","beatport.com/label/enormous-tunes/10907"}', 'Zürich-based house and progressive house label founded 2005. Home to Nora En Pure. Active 2025 releases (''The Yearbook 2025''). LabelRadar portal open. Strong Beatport and streaming credibility. Swiss label with global reach in melodic/progressive house.', '2026-06-01'),

