  ('Tomorrowland Music', 'elite', 'needs_warm_intro', 'form', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/tomorrowlandacademy/portal', '{"house","tech-house","big-room","festival-house","melodic-techno"}', null, null, 'Submit to Tomorrowland Academy (open demo portal) as entry point to Tomorrowland Music ecosystem LabelRadar portal for Tomorrowland Academy confirmed in search results and listed as active. Note: portal slug is ''tomorrowlandacademy'' not ''tomorrowlandmusic''. Beatport confirms label active.', '{"labelradar.com/labels/tomorrowlandacademy/portal","labelradar.com/labels/tomorrowlandacademy/profile","beatportal.com/articles/630237-tomorrowland-academy-unveils-exciting-plastik-funk-remix-competition"}', 'Official label of the world''s most prestigious electronic music festival. Active 2025 releases on Beatport featuring Afrojack, R3HAB, Timmy Trumpet. Massive streaming credibility. Tomorrowland Academy sublabel accepts demos openly; main label appears to require existing relationships.', '2026-06-01'),

