  ('Sudbeat Music', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@sudbeat.com', '{"progressive-house","melodic-techno","deep-progressive"}', null, null, 'Use private SoundCloud links only demos@sudbeat.com confirmed as official A&R email on labelsbase which cites official sources. Hernan Cattaneo''s label, active and well-known.', '{"labelsbase.net/sudbeat-music","ra.co/labels/2584"}', 'Hernan Cattaneo''s flagship label — one of the most respected progressive house imprints globally. Consistently charts on Beatport, releases from GMJ, Franky Wah, and many emerging South American and international artists. Strong Beatport and streaming presence. Active through 2025.', '2026-06-01'),

