  ('Steyoyoke', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.steyoyoke.com/submit-your-demo/', '{"melodic-house","melodic-techno","organic-house","progressive-house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud playlist links ONLY. Music must be submitted EXCLUSIVELY to Steyoyoke — no simultaneous submissions to other labels or DJs. Select from: Steyoyoke, Steyoyoke Black, or Inner Symphony Official submission form confirmed directly on steyoyoke.com/submit-your-demo/. High confidence. Exclusivity clause is unusual — read carefully before submitting.', '{"steyoyoke.com/submit-your-demo","labelsbase.net/steyoyoke","ra.co/labels/7514"}', 'Berlin label founded by Soul Button with three imprints (Steyoyoke, Steyoyoke Black, Inner Symphony). Active Beatport presence, dedicated submission form on own website — one of the most transparent submission processes in this slice. Releases melodic/organic and ethereal techno.', '2026-06-01'),

