  ('Ovum Recordings', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://ovumrecordings.com/contact-2/', '{"house","tech-house","techno"}', null, null, 'Submit via the official site''s ''Submit a Demo''. Postal A&R also accepted: Ovum Recordings, 611 S. 4th St, Philadelphia, PA 19147, Attn: A&R Official ovumrecordings.com/contact-2/ has a contact form (no public demo email listed); general label email ovum@ovum-rec.com exists but not a demo-specific channel. Corrected url from homepage to specific contact page.', '{"ovumrecordings.com/contact-2","ovumrecordings.com"}', 'Josh Wink''s seminal Philadelphia label (since 1994) — deep house/techno heritage and respect.', '2026-06-01'),

