  ('Só Track Boa', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@sotrackboa.com', '{"tech-house","house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only Confirmed by labelsbase as the A&R demo email. General contact is contato@sotrackboa.com.', '{"labelsbase.net/so-track-boa","soundcloud.com/sotrackboa"}', 'Major Brazilian tech house brand (Vintage Culture''s circle) — huge reach in the LATAM scene.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Warung Recordings', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://tstack.app/warung-rec', '{"melodic-house","tech-house","organic-house"}', null, null, 'Submit via the Trackstack portal (or the demo email)', '{"tstack.app/warung-rec","soundcloud.com/warungrecordings"}', 'Warung Beach Club''s label (Brazil, since 2012) — a globally respected melodic/organic platform.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Apparel Music', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demo@apparelmusic.com', '{"deep-house","jazzy-house","house","nu-disco"}', null, null, 'General contact: info@apparelmusic.com. Sub-label Apparel Tronic handles more electronic/downtempo material.', '{"apparelmusic.com/about","labelsbase.net/apparel-music","beatport.com/label/apparel-music/14885/releases","apparelmusic.bandcamp.com/album/apparel-music-b-day-15"}', 'Milan-based independent label founded in 2009 by Kisk; pioneered the jazz-meets-deep-house sound. Over 15 years of releases with genuine global distribution (Beatport, Traxsource). Released 15th anniversary compilation in Aug 2025 featuring artists from Italy, USA, Australia, Spain and Germany. Plausible career launchpad for an unknown with a soulful, jazz-inflected sound.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Jackies Music Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@jackiesmusic.com', '{"house","deep-house","soulful-house"}', null, null, 'Official label page also lists steve@jackiesmusic.com as the label management contact. Both emails appear valid for submissions.', '{"jackiesmusic.com/label","jackiesmusicrecords.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/24917","demolist.app/label_profile/jackies-music-records"}', 'Independent Barcelona house label launched June 2023 with 34+ releases to date. Closely linked to the Off Sónar ecosystem – released an Off Barcelona 2025 Sampler. Has signed Moon Boots, Piero Pirupa, DJ Lora and Keys N Krates, demonstrating real curator credibility. Young label hungry for new talent in the Barcelona house scene.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Sincopat', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@sincopat.com', '{"tech-house","deep-house","progressive-house","electronica"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only Also has a LabelRadar portal. General contact: info@sincopat.com.', '{"labelsbase.net/sincopat","sincopat.com","ra.co/labels/4493","essentialhouse.club/2024/12/va-2024-day-collection-on-sincopat"}', 'Valencia, Spain-based label founded 2010 by AFFKT; widely regarded as one of Spain''s finest avant-garde electronic imprints with 100+ releases. Active in 2025 with seasonal compilations (Day / Night collections). Has collaborated with LabelRadar for remix contests indicating openness to unknown talent. Strong Beatport/Traxsource presence. Can genuinely shift a career for an artist in the experimental tech-house space.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Pornostar Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demo@pornostarrecords.com', '{"funky-house","nu-disco","afro-house","jackin-house","house"}', null, null, 'SoundCloud links only Email corroborated by search results citing official policy; label active with multiple 2025 releases on Beatport', '{"pornostarrecords.com","beatport.com/release/lets-play-house-2025-amstersam-edit/5455681"}', 'Spain-based (Barcelona-affiliated) house label ranked #1 Funky House label on BeatStats with 410,708+ points. Releases weekly across Beatport and Traxsource covering Funky House, Nu Disco, Tribal and Afro House. Roster includes Block & Crown, Crazibiza, Nicola Fasano. Released annual ''Funky House Annual 2025'' and ''Funky House Annual 2026'' compilations showing consistent output. High viability for funky/jackin-house adjacent demos.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Mood Funk Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.moodfunkrecords.com/contacts/', '{"jackin-house","funky-house","house","tech-house"}', null, null, 'Official site has a ''Submit Your Demo'' form. Also accepts emails with SoundCloud private links. General info: info@moodfunkrecords.com.', '{"moodfunkrecords.com","moodfunkrecords.com/contacts","traxsource.com/label/26419/mood-funk-records","ra.co/labels/13318"}', 'Italian (Sicily) house label founded by Angelo Ferreri; focuses on Funky-Tech-House with 600+ artist roster and global DJ support (Carl Cox, Roger Sanchez et al.). Actively releasing in 2025 with tracks by Joaquin Phunk, Hiva, Diego Serrao. Has a dedicated submission form on official website plus email. Established enough to give unknown artists real dancefloor exposure.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Hell Yeah Recordings', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://hellyeahrec.bandcamp.com/contact', '{"balearic-house","nu-disco","minimal","tech-house","electronica"}', null, null, 'Italian label active with releases through 2025 (Balearic/disco/house). Claimed URL was a malformed Bandcamp contact URL. Corrected to the clean Bandcamp contact form URL. No dedicated demo email found.', '{"hellyeahrec.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/1136"}', 'Italian label (Ferrara) founded 2006 by Marco ''peeDoo'' Gallerani; descended from Mantra Vibes, one of Italy''s leading dance labels. Active releases in 2025 including ''File Under Balearic Gabba Vol 2'' (March 2025) and ''Recess EP'' by Johan Blende (December 2025). Known for eclectic Balearic, modern-disco-ish sound. Featured in Juno Daily label focus March 2025. A real launchpad for artists with a Balearic/disco-house sensibility.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Polifonic Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'hello@polifonic.it', '{"house","melodic-house","electronica","organic-house"}', null, null, 'Email is the general/all-purpose contact per the official label page (polifonic.it/label/). No separate demo address listed.', '{"polifonic.it/label","polifonic.bandcamp.com","ra.co/news/74652"}', 'Puglia (Itria Valley), Italy-based label born from the acclaimed annual Polifonic festival (since 2017). Label launched 2021 and released 9 titles including vinyl. Active in 2025 with ''Magnolia EP'' by Damiano Von Erckert (July 2025). Releases span house, acid and electronica with a strong Puglian/Italian identity. The festival connection gives signed artists rare event placement and press opportunities.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Memento Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'hello@mementolabel.com', '{"minimal","deep-house","house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only hello@mementolabel.com confirmed on labelsbase.net and corroborated by proshare/secondary references. Genre is tech house; label based in Mantova, Italy. Founded 2011.', '{"labelsbase.net/memento","mementorecords.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/5341"}', 'Italian label (Mantua/Bologna area) founded 2006 by Algerian-Italian DJ Idriss D; 56+ catalog numbers with releases through September 2024 (EP Memento052). Operates from the fertile Pianura Padana music region. Known for discovering local Italian talent. Active in the minimal/deep house space, respected within the European underground circuit.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Be One Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@beonerecords.com', '{"tech-house","minimal","house","afro-house"}', null, null, 'demos@beonerecords.com and form at beonerecords.com/demos/ confirmed by labelsbase. Two channels available.', '{"labelsbase.net/be-one-records","beatport.com/label/be-one-records/19923"}', 'Spain-based (Granada/Barcelona) label run by producer-DJ Ruiz dB. Active on Beatport and Traxsource with a ''Best of 2024'' compilation released. Focuses on tech house, minimal and afro house. Has a dedicated demos page and email. Entry-level label within the Spanish underground scene that can provide a release credit and distribution footprint for an unknown artist.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Prospect Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demo@prospectrec.it', '{"tech-house","techno","deep-house","minimal"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only General contact: info@prospectrec.it. Label website and Bandcamp: prospectrec.bandcamp.com.', '{"labelsbase.net/prospect-records","prospectrec.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/6223","traxsource.com/label/14404/prospect-records"}', 'Naples, Italy-based label founded 2011 by respected Italian DJ/producer Hollen; releases span tech house, minimal and techno. Demonstrably active in 2024-2025 with Hollen ''Feel Alive'' (Jan 2024), ''Just Be'' (Oct 2024), and ''Night Trip'' (Jan 2025). Has a public domain email for demos. Italian underground credibility with Beatport and Traxsource distribution. Can launch an unknown artist in the Italian/European tech house circuit.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Poker Flat Recordings', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@pokerflat-recordings.com', '{"deep-house","minimal","tech-house","house"}', null, null, 'Private streaming link only — no download links, no public links. No feedback guaranteed if material does not fit Label receives many demos daily; response not guaranteed. Send via private SoundCloud / Dropbox link only.', '{"pokerflat-recordings.com","909originals.com/2024/09/03/steve-bug-on-25-years-of-poker-flat-and-the-challenges-facing-up-and-coming-electronic-artists","pokerflatrecordings.bandcamp.com/album/best-of-poker-flat-recordings-2024"}', 'Steve Bug''s 25-year Berlin institution; one of Germany''s most respected underground house / minimal labels, artists like Sebo K, Isolée and Huxley came through here. Has a direct demo email on the official site, 2024–2025 active with Best Of 2024 compilation and new collabs in May 2025.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Sublease Music', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'subleasedemo@pokerflat-recordings.com', '{"deep-house","minimal","tech-house","house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links preferred Sub-label of Poker Flat Recordings. Focused on deeper, more tracky, club-ready material. Strong new-talent mandate.', '{"electronicgroove.com/steve-bug-presents-new-label-sublease-music","essentialhouse.club/2025/03/steve-bug-herve-solar-lift-off-on-sublease-music","subleasemusic.bandcamp.com"}', 'Poker Flat''s sub-label for ''reduced, hypnotic, raw'' club cuts; explicitly created to break new talent alongside Poker Flat main roster. Active: Sublease Music Vol.04 Dec 2024, Vol.05 2025, Steve Bug & Hervé Solar ''Lift Off'' March 2025. Has its own dedicated demo email separate from Poker Flat.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Upon.You Records', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demo@uponyou-records.com', '{"tech-house","minimal","deep-house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only General contact info@uponyou-records.com. Booking: booking@uponyou-records.com. Phone: +49 (0) 30 4208 4573.', '{"labelsbase.net/upon-you-records","electrobuzz.net/2024/12/marco-resmann-cari-golden-the-algorithm-anniversary-mix-on-upon-you-records/662168","uponyou-records.com"}', 'Respected Berlin institution (est. 2007) run by Marco Resmann and Hawks Grunert; launched Cari Golden, Luna City Express, HYPOXIA LDN and many others. Active December 2024 (Algorithm Anniversary Mix with Cari Golden) and June 2025 (Dance Ma Sense Cocolino Remix). Consistent quality bar for underground Berlin tech house/minimal.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Great Stuff Recordings', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://tstack.app/great-stuff-recordings', '{"tech-house","house","minimal-/-deep-tech"}', null, null, 'Verified Trackstack portal from official Great Stuff Facebook post: ''Send your demos to https://tstack.app/great-stuff-recordings''. General contact also: mail@greatstuff.eu.', '{"facebook.com/GreatStuffRec/posts/get-involved-send-your-demos-to-httpststackappgreat-stuff-recordings/1146478717043041","electrobuzz.net/2025/12/va-the-gems-of-2025-on-great-stuff-recordings/834050","greatstuffrec.bandcamp.com"}', 'Munich-based label est. 2003, part of Housesession label group; one of Germany''s highest-volume tech house labels (1400+ Beatport tracks). Active across 2024–2025 with Amsterdam 2024 compilation, ''Gems of 2025'' VA, and Summer Anthems 2025 Vol.2. Official Trackstack portal confirmed from their own Facebook post.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Parquet Recordings', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@parquet-recordings.com', '{"deep-house","melodic-house","tech-house","progressive-house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only General contact info@parquet-recordings.com. Booking: booking@parquet-recordings.com. Label focuses on melodic, intelligent, accessible deep/tech house and progressive elements.', '{"labelsbase.net/parquet-recordings","beatportal.com/articles/188488-label-of-the-month-parquet-recordings","beatport.com/label/parquet-recordings/3824/releases"}', 'Solee''s German label est. 2006; 200+ releases, Beatport ''Label of the Month'', regular Beatport Progressive/Deep House Top 10s. Active February 2025 (AYU - Reach the Sky release) and returning 2025 with stated new direction into melodic house & techno. Accessible to unknown artists through direct demo email listed on labelsbase.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Uncanny Valley', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'info@uncannyvalley.de', '{"house","minimal","deep-house","acid-house","funk"}', null, null, 'Send SoundCloud link to info@uncannyvalley.de. Be patient — team has limited time due to other employment Label also prefers in-person introductions at events in Dresden and beyond. No response should not be taken personally. Sub-labels: shtum Records, credit00ratlife.', '{"uncannyvalley.de/about#about-contact","traxsource.com/title/2490518/14-years-of-uncanny-valley","uncannyvalleyrec.bandcamp.com"}', 'Dresden label est. 2010; grown from a friends collective to a respected international underground network with 100+ releases. Active May 2025 (''Put The Funk Back In 2 Techno''), March 2025 (''14 Years of Uncanny Valley'' comp), Feb 2025 (''La Bomba''). Honest, accessible submission policy.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Cécille Records', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.cecille-records.de/', '{"tech-house","minimal","deep-house","house"}', null, null, 'Navigate to DEMO SUBMISSION section on official website cecille-records.de Official cecille-records.de website has a ''DEMO SUBMISSION'' section in navigation, but specific form content was not accessible via fetch. No standalone submission URL confirmed. The claimed_url pointing to cecille-records.de is the right domain. Method appears to be on-site form.', '{"cecille-records.de","linktr.ee/cecillerecords"}', 'Mannheim label est. 2008; defined the ''Mannheim Sound'' with Nick Curly, Leon, Sidney Charles, Reboot. Active 2024–2025 (Reboot ''Red House'' EP, Leyo debut album, Fleur Shore first vinyl, Cécille Summer 2025 Compilation, CECSEASON003 July 2025). Official site has dedicated Demo Submission page in navigation.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Moonbootique Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'hello@moonbootique.com', '{"house","electro-house","tech-house","melodic-house"}', null, null, 'Streaming links only — no MP3 attachments Simple email submission. No attachment policy enforced. Label prefers links over files.', '{"labelsbase.net/moonbootique","beatport.com/label/moonbootique/14080","moonbootique.com"}', 'Hamburg label est. 2001 by Moonbootica; one of Germany''s longest-running independent house imprints. Active 2024–2025: ''Can''t Stop Me'' April 2025, ''Burning'' December 2025, releases in 2026 confirmed. Artists include Township Rebellion, Ante Perry, Julian Wassermann, David Hasert. Submission email confirmed via multiple sources.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('LOSSLESS', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'hello@lossless.cc', '{"deep-house","minimal","melodic-house"}', null, null, 'hello@lossless.cc confirmed as the label contact email across multiple sources. Berlin-based label run by Mathias Schober and Thomas Herb. Bandcamp page is active.', '{"losslesscc.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/11173","proshare.audio/lossless"}', 'Berlin label est. 2014 run by Mathias Schober and Thomas Herb; known for elegant modern deep house with roster including Frankey & Sandrino, Manuel Tur, Love over Entropy, David Kochs. Active 2024–2025: catalog at LL1237/LL1238 (Jepe ''Sunny/Fantasia'', Soudant ''Futility EP''). Boutique scale where a signed track has genuine scene impact.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Snork Enterprises', 'b', 'needs_warm_intro', 'dm', 'https://snorkenterprises.bandcamp.com/', '{"minimal","tech-house","minimal-/-deep-tech"}', null, null, 'Label active with Clark Davis ''Berlin'' EP released Nov 2024 (within 2 years); demo method listed as DM via Bandcamp/SoundCloud; genre is atmospheric minimal, tech-house and techno', '{"snorkenterprises.bandcamp.com","electrobuzz.net/2025/02/clark-davis-berlin-on-snork-enterprises/680349"}', 'Hamburg label est. 2004 run by Christian Schachta; niche underground imprint with loyal following for atmospheric minimal-techhouse. Active July 2024 (Luis Luchetti ''Siqy'', Chris Baumann ''State of Flux'') and Feb 2025 (vinyl session at BaalSaal Hamburg). No public demo inbox — label is curated by owner personally.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Public Possession', 'a', 'needs_warm_intro', 'dm', 'https://www.publicpossession.com/', '{"house","disco","deep-house","indie-dance"}', null, null, 'Munich independent label/shop run by Marvin and Valentino. Official site returned 403 during fetch. No public demo submission channel confirmed. General shop email shop@publicpossession.com found but not confirmed as demo channel. Claimed method ''dm'' cannot be verified against specific channel.', '{"publicpossession.com","publicpossession.bandcamp.com/music"}', 'Munich label est. 2013 run by Valentino Betz and Marvin Schuhmann; internationally regarded for its eclectic house, disco and world-music-influenced releases. Event at Haus der Kunst May 2024; active releases ongoing. Boutique output where each release carries significant press and scene impact. No open demo inbox — relationship-driven.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Boogie Angst', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'info@boogieangst.com', '{"nu-disco","indie-dance","deep-house","funk"}', null, null, 'info@boogieangst.com confirmed on official site boogieangst.com as the sole public contact. No separate demos@ address. Label active through 2025 (September 2025 Kraak & Smaak release). Genre: indie dance / nu disco / house.', '{"boogieangst.com","essentialhouse.club/2025/11/moods-august-charles-wildfire-on-boogie-angst"}', 'Netherlands label (Amsterdam area) with strong Kraak & Smaak and Fouk connection; known for nu-disco, funk-influenced electronic dance releases. Active 2024–2025: Edition Four March 2024, ''Heat'' March 2025, ''Nothing Is Forever'' July 2025, Moods ''Wildfire'' Nov 2025. Good entry point for disco-house / nu-disco crossover material.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Unknown To The Unknown (UTTU)', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'yo@uttu.club', '{"deep-house","uk-bass","house","breaks","garage","jungle"}', null, null, 'Email verified directly from official uttu.club website. Hot Haus Recs shares the same contact. Label recently merged online presence to uttu.club.', '{"uttu.club","unknowntotheunknown.bandcamp.com","soundcloud.com/uttuclub"}', 'Seminal UK underground electronic label run by DJ Haus. Launched careers of Mall Grab, DJ Boring, VTSS and others. Sits at the intersection of UK bass, house, garage and breaks — a career-making imprint for an unknown artist breaking from the underground.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Hot Haus Recs', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'yo@uttu.club', '{"house","uk-bass","bassline","deep-house","bass-house"}', null, null, 'Shares submission contact with UTTU via official uttu.club site. Confirmed via direct fetch of uttu.club. Recent releases March 2025 (John Heaven ''Ow''), Dec 2024 (lau.ra ''Vibe'').', '{"uttu.club","beatport.com/label/hot-haus-recs/32923/releases","ra.co/labels/10275"}', 'Sister label to UTTU focused on rawer house, bass and UK-influenced sounds. Active with releases in 2024-2025 including John Heaven ''Ow'' (Mar 2025), lau.ra ''Vibe'' (Dec 2024), Frazer Ray & BRUX (Mar 2025). Has broken multiple unknown artists into the UK underground circuit.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Banoffee Pies Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'banoffeepies.music@gmail.com', '{"deep-house","lo-fi-house","bass","electronica","experimental-house"}', null, null, 'Email sourced from official Facebook page (facebook.com/wearebanoffeepies/) and confirmed via multiple independent searches. Booking/general inquiries: info.banoffeepies@gmail.com. Distribution via !K7. Bandcamp contact form also available.', '{"banoffeepiesrecords.bandcamp.com","facebook.com/wearebanoffeepies","beatport.com/label/banoffee-pies-records/61526/releases"}', 'Bristol-born, now Berlin-based multi-medium label founded 2014 by Ell Weston. Distributed by !K7. Home to Ciel, D. Tiffany, Pugilist, Xades and others. One of the most respected underground deep/lo-fi labels in the UK-global circuit. Active Feb 2025 (Xades ''Vapour'', BP027D).', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Edible Records', 'a', 'needs_warm_intro', 'form', 'https://edible-music.bandcamp.com/', '{"house","tech-house","disco-house","bass-house"}', null, null, 'Use official Bandcamp contact form Contact available via Bandcamp contact form. Label confirmed active through 2025 (Tony Romera ''La Police'' Jul 2025). No dedicated demo email found publicly.', '{"edible-music.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/14303"}', 'Bristol-based label co-founded by Eats Everything and former NRK boss Nick Harris (2015). Releases from Lord Leopard, Mele, Seb Zito, Waze & Odyssey, Illyus & Barrientos, Tony Romera ''La Police'' (Jul 2025). One of the most profile-raising house labels in the UK.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Futureboogie Recordings', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://futureboogie-recordings.bandcamp.com/', '{"deep-house","disco","house","nu-disco"}', null, null, 'Contact via Bandcamp form or Instagram @futureboogierecordings Label is active (releases confirmed in 2024-2025, including January 2025 release). No public demo email found. The Bandcamp page has a generic contact form. Claimed method ''form'' and URL pointing to Bandcamp is the best available channel.', '{"futureboogie-recordings.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/6103"}', 'Bristol-based agency and club night turned label. Released Julio Bashmore''s debut and consistently champions quality deep/disco house. Active through Jan 2025 (Enzio Etchaberri, release #144). Respected imprint that can meaningfully expose an unknown UK artist.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Warehouse Music', 'a', 'needs_warm_intro', 'email', null, '{"tech-house","uk-minimal","house","bassline"}', null, null, 'The input sources reference RA label 15235 (Mella Dee''s UK techno Warehouse Music, est. 2017) but the claimed linktr.ee URL contains no demo submission info. Note: there is a separate German deep-house label also called ''Warehouse Music'' (labelsbase) accepting demos at warehouse.music@gmx.de — these are two distinct labels. For Mella Dee''s imprint (RA 15235) no public demo channel could be confirmed. Do not assign the German label''s email to this entry.', '{"ra.co/labels/15235","linktr.ee/warehousemusic"}', 'London-based imprint by Mella Dee, one of the UK''s most respected underground tech house/UK minimal producers. WM001-WM024+ releases; roster includes Spencer Parker, L-Vis 1990, Joshua James, BLACK GIRL/WHITE GIRL. UK Minimal Vol. 1 & 2 (Oct-Dec 2025) confirms very strong activity.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('ec2a', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@ec2aworldwide.com', '{"uk-bass","tech-house","house","bassline","uk-garage-adjacent-club"}', null, null, 'Use Bandcamp contact form or reach via Instagram @ec2a_ Official ec2aworldwide.com/pages/contact-us-1 explicitly lists ''Demos: demos@ec2aworldwide.com''; claimed method (form) and url (ec2a.bandcamp.com) were incorrect. Corrected to email via official contact page.', '{"ec2aworldwide.com/pages/contact-us-1"}', 'London underground label operated by Dr Dubplate with tagline ''Making way for the new wave.'' Rinse FM bi-monthly residency. Releases INVT, Soul Mass Transit System and others. UK bass/house crossover. Active 2024 with DJ Mag Vital Label feature and Corsica Studios event.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('E-Beamz', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'e.beamz.records@gmail.com', '{"deep-house","lo-fi-house","house"}', null, null, 'Email e.beamz.records@gmail.com sourced from aggregator/community references, not directly from official site. Last confirmed original release 2023. 2024 activity was vinyl repress only. Low confidence on current activity — treat as possibly dormant and verify before submitting.', '{"e-beamz.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/14970","clone.nl/all/label/e-beamz+records"}', 'UK South Coast label (est. 2016) co-founded by DJ Haus and Mat Unearthed. Launched DJ Boring''s career with ''Winona''. Roster: DJ Boring, DJ Seinfeld, Hugo Massien, Settle Down, Tommy The Cat, Lake Haze. Last original releases 2023; 2024 activity was vinyl repress only. Included for historical weight; verify activity before submitting.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('2 B REAL', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://2-b-real.bandcamp.com/', '{"uk-club","bass-house","experimental-house","uk-garage-adjacent","freaky-club"}', null, null, 'Contact via Bandcamp form or reach Finn via social media Manchester label by Finn and Local Action, active with releases through 2025. Bandcamp contact form is the only confirmed submission channel. No dedicated demo email found publicly.', '{"2-b-real.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/16786"}', 'Manchester-based experimental club label run by Finn and Local Action. Roster: Anz, Gage, Clemency, Iceboy Violet, Martyn Bootyspoon, aya. Cutting-edge UK bass-house crossover with DJ Mag coverage. Active Feb 2025 (Dismal House II: Dismal Inferno). North-West UK perspective.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Product London Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.productlondon.com/send-us-demos/', '{"house","tech-house","techno"}', null, null, 'Submit via web form at productlondon.com/send-us-demos/. Use private SoundCloud links — no download links. Listen to back catalogue first to confirm genre fit. Demos reviewed once per week — no reply means not a fit Demo submission form verified directly from productlondon.com/send-us-demos/ via WebFetch. Form requires: Name, Email, Message with track links, optional Phone. All demos heard per label statement.', '{"productlondon.com/send-us-demos","beatport.com/label/product-london-records/34542"}', 'London-based label with a transparent, artist-friendly cold-submission process. Explicitly accepts all demos via web form, reviews weekly, and states all submitted demos are heard. Focused on house and techno. Active on Beatport with a growing catalog. Excellent entry-point for unknown UK producers.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Hessle Audio', 'elite', 'needs_warm_intro', 'email', 'info@hessleaudio.com', '{"deep-house","uk-bass","leftfield-house","techno-adjacent","experimental-club"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only info@hessleaudio.com confirmed on labelsbase.net and cross-referenced via RA/press. Official contact page hessleaudio.com/contact returned 503 at time of fetch. Label active through Oct 2024 (Pearson Sound EP). Genre: UK bass/dubstep/house adjacent.', '{"labelsbase.net/hessle-audio","hessleaudio.com/contact","ra.co/news/81219"}', 'Highly prestigious London/Leeds label (est. 2007) run by Ben UFO, Pearson Sound and Pangaea. Roster: Anz, Pangaea, Pearson Sound, Jasmín. Active with Pearson Sound ''Which Way Is Up'' EP (Oct 2024). One of the most tastemaker-defining labels in UK underground dance — a career-defining placement.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Pacific Rhythm', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://pacificrhythm.org/', '{"deep-house","lo-fi-house","organic-house","electronica"}', null, null, 'Contact via website (pacificrhythm.org) or Bandcamp contact form pacificrhythm.org has an email link (info@pacificrhythm.org) as general contact; no dedicated demo submission form confirmed. Label confirmed active (Canada House Jun 2025, 10 Years compilation Mar 2025).', '{"pacificrhythm.org","pacificrhythm.bandcamp.com"}', 'Vancouver-based label (est. 2013) with strong UK/European following and tastemaker status. Active with 10th anniversary sampler (Mar 2025) featuring LNRDCROY, Khotin, Active Surplus. Roster: D. Tiffany, Space Ghost, Flørist. Highly relevant for UK deep/lo-fi house producers seeking global placement. Investigated per slice instructions.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Innate Recordings', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://innate-recordings.bandcamp.com/', '{"deep-house","deep-electronic","organic-house"}', null, null, 'Contact via Bandcamp form or Instagram @inn8media Label is active (Innate 007 released Oct 2024, Palm Palm remaster scheduled May 2025). No public demo submission email found. Bandcamp has a generic contact link. inn8.net/record-label/ does not list demo contact. Claimed Bandcamp URL is the best available channel.', '{"inn8.net/record-label","innate-recordings.bandcamp.com"}', 'Bristol-based deep electronic label (est. 2018) with a focused, quality-first catalog. Active with Innate 007 (Oct 2024) and upcoming Connective Zone ''Palm Palm'' remaster (May 2025). Distributed by Juno. Specialises in ''deep electronic music with warmth and soul.'' Excellent match for unknown UK deep house artists.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Lost Palms', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScnxR3qcD4b-T2Om0iE0E124hLZYc1a_B51IM37OZUDHlvK9A/viewform?usp=sf_link', '{"deep-house","lo-fi-house","house"}', null, null, 'Use the Shall Not Fade Google Form — explicitly selects Lost Palms as a target label. Provide artist name and Instagram handle. Submit private SoundCloud playlist with as many tracks as possible. List previous label release history Google Form retrieved from linktr.ee/shallnotfade (official Shall Not Fade Linktree). Form confirmed open Jun 2026. The form allows selection of Lost Palms as a target. Sub-label of Shall Not Fade; parent label is in DB but Lost Palms itself is not.', '{"linktr.ee/shallnotfade","docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScnxR3qcD4b-T2Om0iE0E124hLZYc1a_B51IM37OZUDHlvK9A/viewform","ra.co/labels/15390"}', 'Sub-label of Shall Not Fade (also in DB) focused on deeper, dustier house cuts. Roster: DJ Boring, Dylan Dylan, Alex Virgo, Subjoi, Justin Jay, Harrison BDP. Active through 2026. The demo form covers Lost Palms explicitly. A direct way to access the Shall Not Fade ecosystem for deeper house output.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Maya Records', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://tstack.app/maya-records/send', '{"house","tech-house","deep-house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only. Up to 5 tracks via Trackstack Two submission channels confirmed: Trackstack portal (official) and direct email (SoundCloud links only). Both sourced from label''s own social pages and multiple music news sources.', '{"essentialhouse.club/2026/01/joeski-chainless-on-maya-records","essentialhouse.club/2026/02/joeski-music-is-everything-original-on-maya-records","whenwedip.com/2024/04/premiere-joeski-maya-records","electrobuzz.net/2025/01/joeski-spanglish-on-maya-records/667795"}', 'NYC-based house institution founded in 2000 by Joeski. Active through 2026 with confirmed releases: ''Chainless'' (Jan 2026), ''Music Is Everything'' (Feb 2026), ''Take You Higher'' (Mar 2025), ''Spanglish'' (Dec 2024), ''Aliens On Earth'' (Apr 2024). Respected indie that breaks unknown artists within the New York/US underground house circuit. Two confirmed demo channels: Trackstack portal and direct email.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Guesthouse Music', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'info@guesthousemusic.com', '{"house","deep-house","jackin-house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only Confirmed by labelsbase as the A&R demo email. Oakland-based underground house label founded by Mes (Jason Sutton).', '{"labelsbase.net/guesthouse-music","guesthousemusic.com"}', 'Oakland, CA-based underground house label founded 2004. One of the US West Coast''s premier independently distributed house imprints with 300+ vinyl/digital releases and 200+ artist roster. Released ''Best of 2024'' and ''Best of 2025'' compilations confirming active status. Anniversary party April 2025. DJ Mes is widely credited with keeping West Coast jackin'' house alive.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Trax Records', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/TraxRecords/portal', '{"house","deep-house","classic-house","jackin-house"}', null, null, 'Submit via LabelRadar portal or email. Streaming/SoundCloud links preferred Email confirmed from official traxrecords.com/contact-us page under DEMOS CONTACT section. LabelRadar portal confirmed at labelradar.com/labels/TraxRecords/portal. Trackstack also listed at tstack.app/trax-records per Instagram bio.', '{"traxrecords.com/contact-us","labelradar.com/labels/TraxRecords/portal","edmidentity.com/2025/06/22/trax-records-the-40th-anniversary-collection","ra.co/news/82685"}', 'The original home of house music, Chicago, est. 1985. Active 40th anniversary in 2025 with new vinyl (RISING AGAIN, 500-copy limited edition) and digital releases, pairing legends (Frankie Knuckles, Marshall Jefferson) with contemporary artists (Hiroko Yamamura, Analog 87, Jacques x Gregory). Accepting demos via both LabelRadar and direct email. A release on Trax is one of the most historically significant stamps a US house producer can earn.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('DJ International Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://tstack.app/djinternationalrecords', '{"house","classic-house","deep-house"}', null, null, 'Submit via Trackstack portal Legendary Chicago house label (est. 1985, relaunched); Trackstack submission URL corroborated by multiple sources; direct fetch returned 403 (Trackstack requires login) but URL widely cited', '{"djmag.com/news/legendary-chicago-house-label-dj-international-records-relaunches","beatport.com/label/dj-international-records/88915"}', 'Chicago''s legendary founding house label, est. 1985 — home to Frankie Knuckles, Steve Silk Hurley, Farley Jackmaster Funk, Marshall Jefferson. Relaunched 2021 under Last Man Music with Rocky Jones. Actively releasing with catalog on Beatport and historical significance second only to Trax Records in the Chicago house pantheon. A release here carries enormous cultural weight and credibility.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('My Favorite Robot Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'greaseme@myfavoriterobotrecords.com', '{"tech-house","deep-house","electronica"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only Toronto-based tech house/deep house label founded 2008. greaseme@myfavoriterobotrecords.com confirmed by labelsbase.net and corroborated by multiple independent search results.', '{"labelsbase.net/my-favorite-robot-records","beatport.com/label/my-favorite-robot-records/12460"}', 'Toronto, Canada-based tech house / deep house imprint founded 2008 by duo My Favorite Robot (Jared Simms + Voytek Korab). Active 2024-2025 on Beatport with 208 tech house releases, 252 deep house releases. One of Canada''s leading underground tech-house imprints with real credibility in North American and European markets.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Interstellar Recordings (Insomniac)', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://labelinterstellarrecords.label-engine.com/demos', '{"melodic-house","progressive-house","deep-house","melodic-techno"}', null, null, 'Up to 5 tracks via Label Engine form. Artist name, email, and track titles required. Optional social links and 500-char artist message Label Engine form confirmed live and functional. Insomniac also has parent LabelRadar portal (labelradar.com/labels/insomniac/portal). Launched March 2024. Also distinct from older ''Interstellar Records'' label on Beatport ID 80354.', '{"labelinterstellarrecords.label-engine.com/demos","insomniacmusicgroup.com/label/interstellar","freshmusicfreaks.com/exploring-new-horizons-insomniac-records-launches-interstellar-label-for-melodic-house-and-beyond","beatport.com/label/interstellar-recordings-insomniac/120105"}', 'Los Angeles-based imprint under Insomniac Music Group, launched March 2024 as a sanctuary for melodic house, progressive house, deep house and melodic techno. First release by Jeremy Olander. Active 2024-2026 on Beatport with Marsh, Alex Kennon, Just Her, Eynka, Layla Benitez. Insomniac''s scale means excellent distribution, sync, and event placement. The Label Engine form is a confirmed open submission portal.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Wolf + Lamb Records', 'a', 'needs_warm_intro', 'dm', 'https://wolflambrecords.bandcamp.com/', '{"deep-house","house","indie-dance","nu-disco"}', null, null, 'Contact via Bandcamp ''Contact Wolf + Lamb Records'' email link. No public demo process — DM or industry intro preferred Label active through 2024-2025 per Beatport search results (releases in 2023, 2024, 2025). Claimed method=dm via Bandcamp contact form is consistent with their Bandcamp presence. No public demo email found on any source.', '{"wolflambrecords.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/1763","beatport.com/label/wolf-lamb-records/12379"}', 'Brooklyn, NY label founded ~2005. Home to Lorenzo Dada, No Regular Play, Nick Monaco, PillowTalk. Active through early 2024 with release ''Lost In This Moment'' (Aug 2023) and re-release on Bleep (Mar 2024). The Brooklyn underground deep house sound they pioneered remains highly influential and is a clear trajectory-changer. No open demo portal — relationship-driven access but worth including for its brand power.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Double Standard Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'https://doublestandardrecords.bandcamp.com/', '{"deep-house","house","nu-disco"}', null, null, 'Contact via Bandcamp ''Send an email to Double Standard Records'' link No standalone public demo email found. Bandcamp contact confirmed as the recommended cold approach. Parent label Wolf + Lamb shares contact ecosystem. Low confidence on active response rate — small boutique operation.', '{"doublestandardrecords.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/13148"}', 'Brooklyn/NYC deep house label founded 2010 by Gadi Mizrahi (Baby Prince), off-shoot of Wolf + Lamb. Houses the Wolf + Lamb movement''s funkier, deep-house-forward output, with artists like Soul Clap, Greg Paulus and Edwin Esco. Active with Bandcamp presence and Beatport catalog. Part of the Crew Love coalition. NYC deep house touchstone label.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Crew Love Records', 'b', 'needs_warm_intro', 'dm', 'https://crewlove.bandcamp.com/', '{"deep-house","house","indie-dance","nu-disco"}', null, null, 'No public demo channel — target via affiliated labels (Soul Clap: records@soulclap.us) or DM artists on social media No standalone public demo submission channel found. Joint venture of Wolf + Lamb, Soul Clap, and Double Standard. Active releases confirmed 2026 on Beatport. Best approach: submit to Soul Clap Records first.', '{"ra.co/labels/13148","crewlove.bandcamp.com","beatport.com/label/crew-love-records/53693"}', 'Brooklyn-based collaborative label from Wolf + Lamb, Soul Clap, and Double Standard. Active 2022-2026 on Beatport spanning deep house, house, indie dance, nu-disco. Artists: No Regular Play, PillowTalk, Nick Monaco, Life on Planets, Navid Izadi, Slow Hands. A curated, quality-first imprint that is part of the NYC deep house ecosystem. Access is through the Wolf + Lamb / Soul Clap artist network.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Turbo Recordings', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@turborecordings.com', '{"tech-house","house","indie-dance","electronica"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only demos@turborecordings.com confirmed by labelsbase.net. Turbo Recordings is an active Montreal-based label (Tiga, founded 1998) spanning house, techno, electro.', '{"labelsbase.net/turbo-recordings","turborecordings.bandcamp.com"}', 'Montreal, Canada imprint founded 1998 by Tiga, named Beatport Label of the Month August 2024. Active through 2024-2025 with releases: Dense & Pika ''It House'' (Nov 2024), Extrawelt ''Grindmaster'' (Dec 2024), Kenny Glasgow (Jan 2025). A prestigious Canadian label with real industry clout across tech house, indie dance, and experimental electronic music. Confirmed public demo email.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Phunk Junk Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://phunkjunk.label-engine.com/demos', '{"house","tech-house","deep-house"}', null, null, 'Up to 5 tracks via Label Engine form. Artist name, email, and track titles required Label Engine form confirmed live. Email sourced from labelsbase.net and official website phunkjunk.com. Active 2024-2025 releases confirmed on Beatport.', '{"labelsbase.net/phunkjunk","phunkjunk.label-engine.com/demos","beatport.com/label/phunk-junk-records/25736"}', 'Chicago-based label founded 2012 by producer SALADIN. Active 2024-2025 with releases including ''Get On The Floor'' (Jun 2024, Tech House) and ''Dance With Me'' (Jan 2025, Bass House) on Beatport. A platform rooted in the birthplace of house music, Chicago, with open and confirmed demo submission. A real opportunity for an unknown artist to get heard by a home-grown Chicago label.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Rawhouse Records Chicago', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'dm', 'https://rawhouserecords.bandcamp.com/', '{"house","deep-house","chicago-house","afro-house","nu-disco"}', null, null, 'Contact via Bandcamp ''Contact Rawhouse Records Chicago'' email link Label is active (Jeanette Thomas ''Good Vibrations'' released March 2025). No public demo email or DM submission page found. Bandcamp has a generic contact link. Claimed method ''dm'' and Bandcamp URL are the best available channels.', '{"essentialhouse.club/2025/03/jeanette-thomas-good-vibrations-on-rawhouse-records-chicago","rawhouserecords.bandcamp.com"}', 'Chicago house label founded 2005 by Allen Wright Jr. Specializes in Chicago House, Deep House, Disco House, Nu Disco, Afro-House. Active through 2025 with confirmed releases: Jeanette Thomas ''Good Vibrations'' (March 2025), MISS. TC release (July 2024). A genuine Chicago underground imprint with multiple sub-styles and Traxsource/Beatport presence. A grassroots label that can launch an unknown artist into the Chicago house scene.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Soul Candi Records', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://soulcandi.co.za/submit-a-demo/', '{"afro-house","deep-house","tech-house","afro-tech"}', null, null, 'Original unreleased material only. No remixes or bootlegs. MP3 320kbps preferred, max 20MB per file. Upload via official website form only (no SoundCloud or Dropbox links). Filename must include artist name and track title No response within 8 weeks means not proceeding. WhatsApp contact: +27 82 048 3725.', '{"soulcandi.co.za/submit-a-demo","ra.co/labels/5518","soulcandi.co.za/all-releases"}', 'South Africa''s longest-running dedicated house imprint (est. late 1990s), consistently releasing deep house, afro house and afro tech. Active releases confirmed through 2024 and 2025 (multiple Bandcamp releases: ''The Chronic Effect'' Nov 2025, ''House Archives Vol.1'' Sept 2025). Open public demo submission form on official website with clear requirements.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Kunye Records', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/kunye/portal', '{"afro-house","afro-tech"}', null, null, 'Afro House / Afro Tech only Primary submission channel is LabelRadar portal. General contact: info@kunyerecords.com.', '{"kunyerecords.co.za/about-us","beatportal.com/articles/676618-hype-label-of-the-month-kunye-records","labelradar.com/labels/kunye/portal"}', 'Founded 2020 by Shimza (South Africa). Beatport Hype Label of the Month October 2024. Bridges South African emerging producers to global stages. Roster includes Thakzin, Blanka Mazimela, Darque, with remixes by Louie Vega, Mele, Rodriguez Jr. Has official LabelRadar demo portal and a general contact email.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Make The Girls Dance Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://tstack.app/makethegirlsdance', '{"afro-house","tribal-house","house","latin"}', null, null, 'LabelRadar portal also available: https://www.labelradar.com/labels/makethegirlsdancerecords/portal', '{"threads.com/@juanybravo/post/C8bQfZVPUgr","labelradar.com/labels/makethegirlsdancerecords/portal","beatportal.com/articles/780016-afro-house-the-top-selling-tracks-artists-and-labels-of-2024"}', 'Founded 2021 by HUGEL and Juany Bravo. Ranked #2 top-selling Afro House label on Beatport in 2024. Rooted in Tribal and Afro House, Latin grooves, and club culture. Trackstack demo box URL publicly posted on Threads by label manager Juany Bravo. Also has a LabelRadar portal.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Dawn Patrol Records', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', null, null, '{"afro-house","melodic-house","organic-house"}', null, null, 'Melodic house, organic house, or melodic techno preferred. Label is NOT looking for pure afro house singles Claimed URL dawnpatrolmusic.com/contact is WRONG — that site belongs to ''Dawn Patrol Music'', a US-based music licensing/supervision company (not a record label), which explicitly states it is ''not a record label'' and ''not looking for afro house singles''. The actual Dawn Patrol Records is a Brazilian Afro House/Melodic House label founded in 2020 by Maz and Antdot (Beatport ID 84770, Traxsource ID 54577). No public demo submission channel for the actual label could be confirmed. URL removed.', '{"dawnpatrolmusic.com/contact","beatport.com/label/dawn-patrol-records/84770","label-engine.com/news/dawn-patrol-records"}', 'Founded 2020 by Brazilian duo Maz and Antdot. Top-5 best-selling Afro House label on Beatport in 2023 and 2024. ''Povoada'' reached #1 on Beatport Afro House chart. Active release ''Emoriô'' in October 2024. Official contact form on website. Label explicitly states preferred genres via Instagram @dawnpatrol.music.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Afrocentric Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'cory@afrocentricrecords.com', '{"afro-house","deep-house"}', null, null, 'Send private streaming links (MP3). Include contact details in email body. Keep submission short, best tracks first Label is based in Dubai (UAE) but entirely dedicated to African continent artists and sounds.', '{"afrocentricrecords.com/contact","afrocentricrecords.com/about","beatport.com/label/afrocentric-records/67263"}', 'Founded 2015 by Cory Centric, dedicated exclusively to high-quality Afro House from across the African continent. Active 2024 releases confirmed (RAWNIK ''AMAZWI'', Kates Le Cafe). Demo email published directly on the label''s official contact page.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Cafe De Anatolia', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/CafeDeAnatolia/portal', '{"organic-house","afro-house","ethnic-deep-house","world-music"}', null, null, 'Organic house / ethnic deep house / afro house / world music genres only Also contactable via demos.cafedeanatolia@gmail.com (verified via official Facebook post). LabelRadar portal is the primary channel.', '{"labelradar.com/labels/CafeDeAnatolia/portal","cafe-de-anatolia.com/about","m.facebook.com/CafeDeAnatolia/photos/a.298848046902916/2270135376440830"}', 'Founded 2017, North Macedonia. #1 best-selling label and artist in Organic/Ethnic House on Beatport in 2024. Nominated IMS Ibiza Beatport Hype Label of Year 2024. 10,000+ track catalog with 5,000+ artists across 50+ sub-brands including Afro House. Massive breakout vehicle for unknown artists. LabelRadar portal and email both verified.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Nulu Music', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demo@nulumusic.com', '{"afro-house","afro-tech","deep-house"}', null, null, 'Afro house and afro tech only Booking: booking@nulumusic.com. Sub-label Nulu Electronic also active on Beatport.', '{"nulumusic.com/contact","beatport.com/label/nulu-music/12789/releases","news.traxsource.com/articles/2580/label-spotlight-022-nulu"}', 'Founded 2009 in New York by Anane Vega, pioneer of Afro House and Afro Tech. ''You''re So Sweet'' remix ranked #1 on Traxsource Afro House. Active 2024-2025 releases confirmed (Dec 2024, Nov 2024). Also runs the NULU Movement Radio Show on KayaFM (South Africa). Demo email verified on official contact page.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('CamelMusic Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://tally.so/r/68rO1e', '{"tech-house","house","minimal"}', null, null, 'Tech house and house genres only. Submit private SoundCloud links. Include artist name and email address in the form Tally.so demo form verified live on 2026-06-01. Also reachable at camelrecordsgroup@gmail.com.', '{"tally.so/r/68rO1e","labelsbase.net/camelmusic-records","beatport.com/label/camelmusic-records/26750"}', 'Founded 2012, Mendoza, Argentina. Independent Argentine underground label dedicated to house, tech house and minimal. Active 2025 release confirmed (Jan 2025 on Beatport, May 2026 on LabelsBase). Tally.so demo submission form personally verified as live and functioning.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Kazukuta Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'kazukutarecords@gmail.com', '{"afro-house","afro-tech"}', null, null, 'Afro house only kazukutarecords@gmail.com found in footer of official label website kazukuta-records.com; active Afro-house label with recent releases', '{"kazukuta-records.com","beatport.com/label/kazukuta-records/70568"}', 'Founded 2011, Angola — the first electronic music label born in Angola. 266 Afro House tracks on Beatport. Active releases Dec 2024 and Jan 2025 confirmed. DJEFF has released on Spinnin'' Deep and Diplo''s Higher Ground, giving the label international credibility. Email published on official website kazukuta-records.com.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Timeless Moment', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@timelessmoment.com.br', '{"progressive-house","melodic-house","melodic-techno"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only Brazilian melodic/progressive house label founded 2016 by Morttagua. Active with releases in 2025 (Timeless IBIZA 2025). Primary genre is melodic progressive house, adjacent to house/tech-house scope. demos@timelessmoment.com.br confirmed by labelsbase.net and search results. Official site returned 503 during fetch.', '{"labelsbase.net/timelessmoment","ra.co/labels/15220","beatport.com/label/timeless-moment/59941"}', 'Founded 2016, Brazil. Premier melodic/progressive house label from Brazil with global recognition. ''Timeless 2025'' compilation released in 2025. 881 Progressive House releases on Beatport. Support from Solomun, Black Coffee, Pete Tong (BBC Radio 1), Hernan Cattaneo. Demo email confirmed via LabelsBase and label website.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Area Verde', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demo@area-verde.com', '{"progressive-house","melodic-house","melodic-techno"}', null, null, 'SoundCloud secret links only. All tracks in one secret SoundCloud playlist. Maximum 5 tracks. Include text in email body (not just a link) Also has periodic Beatport Hype producer competitions via LabelRadar portal.', '{"labelsbase.net/areaverde","beatportal.com/articles/294210-area-verde-x-beatport-hype-launch-producer-competition","beatport.com/label/area-verde/79254"}', 'Founded 2019, Brazil (IAMT Music Group). One of 5 labels in Beatport Hype accelerator program. Active 2024-2025 with releases including ''Best Melodic & Progressive House 2024'' compilation on Beatport. 213 Progressive House + 92 Melodic House & Techno releases on Beatport. Runs open producer competitions via LabelRadar. Clear public demo email with requirements.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Nube Music Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'data.nubemusic@gmail.com', '{"progressive-house","deep-house","house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only data.nubemusic@gmail.com confirmed on labelsbase.net. Label active through 2024 (Dec 2024 pre-order found). Argentina-based progressive house label founded 2016.', '{"labelsbase.net/nube-music-records","beatport.com/label/nube-music-records/55979","protonradio.com/labels/1157/nube-music-records/releases"}', 'Founded 2016, Argentina. Partners with Proton Label network. Active December 2024 release (pre-order ''Game Over'' EP) confirmed on Beatport. Focuses on progressive house, deep house, and deep techno from Argentine and international artists. Demo email listed on LabelsBase.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Under Pressure Records South Africa', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'soulvarti@gmail.com', '{"afro-house","afro-tech","deep-house"}', null, null, 'Afro house and adjacent deep house only soulvarti@gmail.com is the founder/label head direct contact (Thabo Matebesi / Soul Varti). Label active — UPR Vaults Locks Unchained Vol. III released Oct 2025, Vol. 5 on Beatport. Afro House / Melodic House genre (house-adjacent).', '{"traxsource.com/label/31388/under-pressure-records-south-africa","beatport.com/label/under-pressure-records-south-africa/29547"}', 'Founded 2012 by Soul Varti, influential Afro House label from South Africa. Active releases confirmed through 2025 (UPR Vaults Locks Unchained Vol. III Oct 2025, ''Christina'' Aug 2025). Features South African producers KingTouch, Smallistic, Deep Sen, Hypaphonik, DJ Tears PLK. Contact email cited across multiple licensing and submission reference sources.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Midnight Riot Records', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'yamster70@hotmail.com', '{"nu-disco","disco","balearic","house","boogie","afro-house"}', null, null, 'Private SoundCloud links only. Yam Who personally listens to every demo Same address used for A&R, bookings, and general contact. Hotmail address has been publicly listed on labelsbase and confirmed on the label''s own site as the single demo channel.', '{"labelsbase.net/midnight-riot","midnightriotrecords.co.uk","midnightriotrecords.bandcamp.com/album/various-the-finest-2024"}', 'London''s premier nu-disco/balearic imprint, run by Yam Who? since 2012. Consistently in Traxsource top-200 and lands numerous compilations per year. Actively released throughout 2024-2025 (''The Finest 2024'', ''Set Me Free'', ''Balearic Headspace Vol 7''). Known for breaking unknown disco and house producers — ideal stepping stone for the slice.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Sol Selectas', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'dm', 'https://soundcloud.com/solselectas', '{"organic-house","tribal-house","deep-house","downtempo","afro"}', null, null, 'Send private SoundCloud links via SoundCloud DM only. Send only a few best tracks. Include bio/concept background. Tracks should be mastered, even basic home master. Replies only if interested — be patient No public demo email. SoundCloud DM is the sole confirmed submission channel, per Sabo interview in Progressive Astronaut and official contact page.', '{"progressiveastronaut.com/feature-sabo","solselectas.com/contact","solselectas.bandcamp.com"}', 'NYC-founded, LA-based organic-house powerhouse run by Sabo since 2006. Home of the ''Summer Sol'' and ''Global Entry'' compilation series — key tastemaker releases in the organic/tribal house scene. Active in 2025 (''Pura Sol'', ''Summer Sol X''). Sabo explicitly stated he listens personally to every SoundCloud DM submission.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Maccabi House', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://tstack.app/maccabihouse', '{"melodic-house","deep-house","psychedelic-house","tech-house"}', null, null, 'Primary channel: Trackstack portal at tstack.app/maccabihouse. Alternative: maccabihouse@gmail.com Trackstack portal confirmed via multiple sources. Gmail address referenced alongside Trackstack as secondary contact.', '{"maccabihouse.bandcamp.com","dancingastronaut.com/2024/04/adam-ten-and-mita-gami-bring-maccabi-house-to-coachella","edmidentity.com/2025/03/30/maccabi-house-all-stars-007"}', 'Tel Aviv imprint run by Adam Ten, one of the most internationally hyped melodic/psychedelic house acts of 2024-2025 (Coachella, Insomniac shows). Roster includes Luke Alessi, Rafael, and others. Active releases throughout 2024-2025 (''Like This'' March 2025, ''All Stars 007'' March 2025). Open Trackstack portal confirms they accept cold demos. Music played by Black Coffee, Solomun, FISHER.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('STEREOHYPE', 'a', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'form', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/stereohype/portal', '{"tech-house","house"}', null, null, 'Submit via LabelRadar portal. Label also historically accepted direct email demos per Instagram post (June 2024) but email not confirmed — use LabelRadar as primary LabelRadar portal is the official confirmed channel. Instagram post C8C1gQ-MGLi teased email demos in June 2024 but exact address unconfirmed publicly. LabelRadar rated high confidence.', '{"labelradar.com/labels/stereohype/portal","stereohype.global","instagram.com/stereohypeglobal/p/C8C1gQ-MGLi"}', 'James Hype''s own artist label, founded 2019. One of the most-streamed tech house acts globally. Active releases in 2024-2025 (e.g. ''Behaviour'' feat. A.D.O.R. 2025, ''More Of The Same'' with Tita Lau 2025). Confirmed open LabelRadar demo portal — very accessible for unknown producers seeking a high-profile tech-house co-sign.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Slow Life', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'dm', 'https://soundcloud.com/slow-life', '{"deep-house","progressive-house","tech-house","organic-house"}', null, null, 'Demos only via SoundCloud DM (stated on their social media). info@slowlifemusic.org for general inquiries Multiple sources (labelsbase, RA, Bandcamp community) confirm ''demos only via SoundCloud DM''. Official website slowlifemusic.org confirms info email.', '{"soundcloud.com/slow-life","slowlifemusic.org","ra.co/labels/10437"}', 'Berlin-based collective-label active since 2011, consistently releasing quality deep/progressive house on vinyl. Catalog now past SL041 (April 2025). Niche underground reach: distributed via Redeye, Yoyaku, Newtone. Accepts cold demos purely via SoundCloud DM — accessible entry point for unknown artists with a deep/progressive sound.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Phantasy Sound', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'demos@phantasysound.co.uk', '{"house","indie-dance","electronica","disco","psychedelic"}', null, null, 'Email demos to above address. General/licensing inquiries: phantasyhq@gmail.com Email confirmed directly from official About Us page at shop.phantasysound.co.uk/pages/about-us. The page includes a ''click here'' link resolving to this address.', '{"shop.phantasysound.co.uk/pages/about-us","909originals.com/2024/04/30/roman-flugel-releases-ep-on-erol-alkans-label-phantasy","ra.co/labels/5277"}', 'London label run by DJ legend Erol Alkan since 2007. UK''s most artistically ambitious house-adjacent imprint; roster includes Roman Flügel, Factory Floor, Tom Rowlands. Releases very active in 2024-2025 (Roman Flügel ''No Solutions EP'' Nov 2024, Factory Floor PH153 Jan 2025). Official About Us page links directly to demos@phantasysound.co.uk — genuine cold-demo channel.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Bastard Jazz Recordings', 'b', 'cold_demo_friendly', 'email', 'info@bastardjazz.com', '{"disco","house","nu-disco","dub","afro","downtempo"}', null, null, 'General inquiry email also used for demo submissions info@bastardjazz.com confirmed on official About page bastardjazz.com/bastard-jazz/. No dedicated demos@ address published; use info@ with clear subject line per industry standard.', '{"bastardjazz.com/bastard-jazz","bastardjazz.bandcamp.com","bastardjazz.com/category/new-releases"}', 'Brooklyn-based label since 2001, now one of the most respected independent disco/house imprints in the US. 143+ nu-disco catalog entries on Beatport. Active releases throughout 2025 (Captain Planet & Tony Allen ''Tony''s House'' Aug 2025, Eliot Lipp EP May 2025, Peter Matson Jan 2025). Artists like Lord Echo, Robohands, Illa J. Confirmed cold-demo-friendly via general contact email. Genre overlap strong for disco/Afro/house slice.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('FHUO Records', 'b', 'relationship_only', null, null, '{"deep-house","house","electronica","indie-dance"}', null, null, 'No public demo channel. Label''s own SoundCloud states ''don''t write us at: forheavenuseonly@gmail.com'' — they do not accept unsolicited demos. Relationship/referral only Included for CRM visibility (warm-intro target). Do NOT cold-email. The address forheavenuseonly@gmail.com is intentionally discouraged. Only approach through artist connections.', '{"soundcloud.com/forheavenuseonly-records","fhuo.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/18612"}', 'London imprint by Folamour — one of the most distinctive deep house artists of the era. Active 2024-2025 releases including ''Oyabun'', ''Chapeau rouge'', ''Ordinary Drugs'', and the album ''Movement Therapy'' (2025). Artists like Kimosabe, Madcat, Parviz on roster. Folamour''s taste-making profile means a release here carries significant weight in the European deep house community.', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Pinchy & Friends', 'b', 'needs_warm_intro', null, null, '{"deep-house","downtempo","leftfield","disco","world-music"}', null, null, 'No public demo channel confirmed. Serendeepity distributes label (info@serendeepity.net may be a distribution contact but not a demo channel). Bandcamp contact form or warm intro recommended Label is active (releases in 2024-2025 including Alex Kassian EP August 2024). No demo submission method found on official site (pinchyandfriends.com), Bandcamp community page, or any secondary source. Claimed method was already ''unknown''.', '{"pinchyandfriends.com","pinchyandfriends.bandcamp.com","ra.co/labels/22466"}', 'LA-based vinyl-focused imprint, catalog PF001–PF021+. Releases eclectic leftfield deep house, Afro-influenced, and disco-house. Artists include Alex Kassian, Exotic Gardens, Dreems. Still actively releasing (PF020 Coyote ''Nyabinghi LP'', PF021 ''Afternoon Dubs'' pre-order 2025). Distributed by Serendeepity and respected in the underground. No cold-demo email confirmed publicly.', '2026-06-01')
on conflict (lower(name)) do update set
  tier = excluded.tier, access_path = excluded.access_path,
  submission_method = excluded.submission_method, contact_link = excluded.contact_link,
  genre_tags = excluded.genre_tags, bpm_min = excluded.bpm_min, bpm_max = excluded.bpm_max,
  submission_requirements = excluded.submission_requirements, sources = excluded.sources,
  why = excluded.why, last_verified = excluded.last_verified;


-- ============================================================================
-- >>> promo_contacts.sql
-- ============================================================================
-- ============================================================================
-- DemoTrack — NON-LABEL promotional contacts master (Spec §12, the other half).
-- Radio, blogs/magazines, playlist curators, repost networks, YouTube, podcasts,
-- and PR firms that can get an unknown house/tech-house artist PLAYS & exposure.
-- Standalone & idempotent; mirrors the read-only `labels` master pattern.
-- Run AFTER schema.sql, with the service role.
-- Generated from data/promo_contacts.json. cost flags free/freemium/paid so the
-- artist can prioritise free organic routes. Full provenance in data/promo_contacts.*.
-- ============================================================================

do $$ begin
  if not exists (select 1 from pg_type where typname='promo_category') then
    create type promo_category as enum ('blog', 'magazine', 'playlist_curator', 'podcast', 'pr', 'radio', 'repost_network', 'youtube');
  end if;
end $$;

create table if not exists promo_contacts (
  id                      uuid primary key default gen_random_uuid(),
  name                    text not null,
  category                promo_category not null,
  cost                    text,                        -- free | freemium | paid
  platform                text,
  genre_focus             text[] not null default '{}',
  submission_method       text,                        -- email|form|portal|dm|none-public|unknown
  contact_link            text,                        -- demo email or submission URL
  submission_requirements text,
  reach                   text,
  why                     text,
  sources                 text[] not null default '{}',
  confidence              text,                        -- high | medium | low
  last_verified           date,
  created_at              timestamptz not null default now()
);
create unique index if not exists promo_contacts_name_key on promo_contacts(lower(name));
create index if not exists promo_contacts_category_idx on promo_contacts(category);

alter table promo_contacts enable row level security;
drop policy if exists promo_contacts_read on promo_contacts;
create policy promo_contacts_read on promo_contacts
  for select to authenticated using (true);

insert into promo_contacts
  (name, category, cost, platform, genre_focus, submission_method, contact_link, submission_requirements, reach, why, sources, confidence, last_verified)
values
  ('Data Transmission', 'blog', 'free', 'web', '{"house","tech house","deep tech","techno"}', 'email', 'grahame@datatransmission.co', 'Private SoundCloud link preferred. Include press release and artist bio. House / Tech House / Deep Tech / Techno only for this contact Grahame Farmer handles house/tech-house/deep-tech/techno premieres specifically. Shelley Dodds (shelley@datatransmission.co) handles DnB. Confirmed on official contact page.', '100k+ monthly site visitors; large SoundCloud following', 'One of the UK''s leading online dance music authorities with a dedicated premieres section for house and tech house. Grahame Farmer personally curates house/tech-house premieres, giving unknown acts a real editorial slot with SoundCloud upload and site coverage.', '{"datatransmission.co/contact","beatportal.com/articles/655232-interview-grahame-farmer-founder-data-transmission"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Magnetic Magazine', 'magazine', 'free', 'web', '{"house","tech house","techno","deep house"}', 'email', 'will@magneticmag.com', 'Press release. High-res press photos. Private streaming link. Artist bio and social links Will Vance (Managing Editor) runs this inbox. reviews@magneticmag.com also reaches all staff writers/editors. demo@magneticmag.com for their in-house label submissions. Confirmed on official contact page.', '500k+ monthly unique visitors', 'US-based music and culture magazine with dedicated tech-house track roundups published monthly in 2025. Features premieres and reviews; actively accepts submissions from independent artists and labels. Monthly ''Best Tech House Tracks'' columns give rising artists real visibility.', '{"magneticmag.com/contact","magneticmag.com/2025/05/the-15-best-tech-house-tracks-of-april-2025"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('DJ Mag', 'magazine', 'free', 'web', '{"house","tech house","techno","electronic"}', 'email', 'olivia.stock@djmag.com', 'Press release. High-res artist photo and packshot. Artist bio and social links. Private SoundCloud link with downloads enabled (320kbps) or fatdrop link — no Dropbox/WeTransfer. Pre-order or buy link if applicable. Suggested run date. Pitch window: no earlier than 3 weeks before release; no later than 2 days before Olivia Stock (Digital Staff Writer) confirmed as the premiere contact via official pitch guide at djmag.com. All genres go to her. Include Q&A material if possible. Due to high volume, not all pitches receive a reply.', '3M+ monthly site visitors; global print and digital readership', 'The world''s most widely read DJ and dance music magazine. Premieres one track per day online, featuring lesser-known acts alongside established names. A premiere slot here signals credibility to bookers and labels globally.', '{"djmag.com/information/how-pitch-dj-mag","djmag.com/press"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Mixmag Australia / NZ', 'magazine', 'free', 'web', '{"house","tech house","techno","electronic"}', 'email', 'editorial@mixmag.net.au', 'Brief pitch explaining desired coverage type (premiere / review / playlist / mix). Private streaming link. Press release and bio editorial@mixmag.net.au confirmed on official ANZ contact page and in their open call-for-music article. Curates a monthly SoundCloud premieres playlist (confirmed active in 2025). Accepts unknown artists explicitly.', 'Mixmag global brand; ANZ SoundCloud premiere playlists active 2025', 'Active offshoot of the world''s biggest dance music brand, explicitly calling for music submissions from any artist — known or unknown — for premieres, playlists, mixes, and reviews. Lower bar than UK flagship but carries global Mixmag brand weight and publishes monthly SoundCloud premiere playlists.', '{"mixmag.net.au/page/contact-mixmag","mixmag.net.au/read/mixmag-australia-nz-is-calling-out-for-music-music"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Mixmag (UK / Global)', 'magazine', 'free', 'web', '{"house","tech house","techno","electronic"}', 'email', 'https://mixmag.net/page/contact-mixmag', 'Press release. High-res photos. Private streaming link. Artist bio and socials. Pitch 1 to 3 weeks before release Contact page returned 403 during direct verification. Known email format is firstname@mixmag.net. Staff handling music includes Megan Townsend and Patrick Hinton (Editor). Best approached via a PR firm or by starting with Mixmag ANZ. Confidence set to medium as submission email could not be confirmed from the official page during this research session.', '5M+ monthly unique visitors; 1.4M+ Instagram followers', 'The flagship global dance music magazine reaching 5M+ monthly visitors. Being premiered or reviewed on Mixmag.net is among the most valuable press placements for any house/tech-house artist. Active in 2025 with weekly new music coverage.', '{"mixmag.net/page/contact-mixmag","muckrack.com/media-outlet/mixmag"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('When We Dip', 'blog', 'free', 'web', '{"house","deep house","progressive house","melodic techno"}', 'email', 'promo@whenwedip.com', 'SoundCloud track link preferred. Press release or brief pitch. Desired premiere date promo@whenwedip.com confirmed via RocketReach email-format data and multiple secondary sources. Web contact form also available. Active premiere series confirmed throughout 2025. Leans toward progressive/melodic house rather than peak-time tech house.', 'Established underground readership; active SoundCloud and social channels', 'Active dance music magazine (Montreal / Dublin / Berlin) running frequent exclusive premieres of independent house and progressive tracks. Well-regarded in the underground scene with consistent editorial output throughout 2025. A premier here reaches a tuned-in global audience.', '{"whenwedip.com/contact-us","whenwedip.com/premieres"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Deep House Amsterdam', 'blog', 'free', 'web', '{"deep house","house"}', 'email', 'lex@deephouseamsterdam.com', 'SoundCloud link only (Dropbox not accepted). Listen to DHA AM and DHA FM channels first to understand their sound direction Lex van Aken (Founder/MD) confirmed as submission contact on official contact page. They respond only if interested. Deep house and melodic deep house focus — straightforward tech house may not fit.', '400k+ YouTube subscribers; 200k+ SoundCloud followers', 'Leading Amsterdam-based deep house blog with 400k+ YouTube subscribers and 200k+ SoundCloud followers across DHA AM and DHA FM channels. Features exclusive premieres and label showcases. Active site with 2026 content confirmed. Ideal for deep-leaning house tracks.', '{"deephouseamsterdam.com/contact","soundcloud.com/deep-house-amsterdam"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('The Groove Cartel', 'blog', 'paid', 'web', '{"house","tech house","techno","deep house","progressive house"}', 'email', 'press@thegroovecartel.com', 'Track link. Artist bio. Social links. SubmitHub preferred for guaranteed 48-hour response and feedback press@thegroovecartel.com confirmed via official submission page. SubmitHub profile also available: submithub.com/blog/the-groove-cartel. Also has a Groover profile for paid submission route. Active in 2025.', '50k+ unique monthly visitors; Google News indexed', 'Quintessential electronic music blog and network with 50k+ unique monthly visitors, indexed on Google News. Actively accepts submissions from unknown artists via SubmitHub (guaranteed feedback within 48 hours) and direct email. Strong fit for tech house specifically.', '{"thegroovecartel.com/submit-music","submithub.com/blog/the-groove-cartel"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('EARMILK', 'blog', 'free', 'web', '{"electronic","house","deep house","dance"}', 'portal', 'https://www.submithub.com/blog/earmilk', 'Submit via SubmitHub or Pillargram only. No direct email submissions accepted — filtered automatically Exclusively accepts via SubmitHub (submithub.com/blog/earmilk) or Pillargram (pillargram.com/refer-curator?referCode=EARMILK). Confirmed on earmilk.com/submit-music/. Active site with 2025 content confirmed.', 'Millions of global readers across 110+ countries', 'Global music blog active since late 2000s reaching millions of readers in 110+ countries. Covers electronic dance music with a dedicated electronic section and premieres new tracks. Submission via SubmitHub is straightforward and open to all artists.', '{"earmilk.com/submit-music","earmilk.com/music/electronic"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Decoded Magazine', 'magazine', 'free', 'web', '{"house","techno","deep house","progressive house","melodic techno"}', 'email', 'submit@decodedmagazine.com', 'Include artist bio and press release. Mark clearly as a premiere request in subject line. Address to Ian French for A&R/Editorial/Premiere pitches. Note: they do NOT accept mixes or unreleased material via submit@ — for premieres, pitch to Ian French directly submit@decodedmagazine.com confirmed on official contact page. Ian French is named A&R/Editorial/Premieres contact; Damion Pell is Editor/MD. Site active as of June 2026. Mix of the Month competition also open monthly for unknowns.', 'Established underground readership; active YouTube, SoundCloud, and social channels', 'Underground electronic music magazine with a dedicated premieres section, Mix of the Month competition open to unknowns, and a Discord community for submissions. Active with premieres confirmed through June 2026. Ian French handles A&R, editorial, and premieres.', '{"decodedmagazine.com/contact","decodedmagazine.com/category/premieres"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Le Visiteur Online', 'blog', 'free', 'web', '{"house","deep house","disco house","nu-disco","boogie"}', 'portal', 'https://www.submithub.com/blog/le-visiteur-online', 'Submit via SubmitHub only — direct submissions no longer accepted. Must be house, disco house, nu-disco, or boogie in style Direct submissions discontinued per SoundCloud profile. SubmitHub at submithub.com/blog/le-visiteur-online is the current active channel. Best suited for deep, disco-leaning house; less so for peak-time tech house.', 'Thousands of unique weekly visitors; large SoundCloud following', 'One of the internet''s biggest house and disco authorities, run by UK DJ/producer/blogger John Hutchison. Receives thousands of unique visitors weekly. Features premieres, interviews, and mixes. SubmitHub is now the only submission route.', '{"submithub.com/blog/le-visiteur-online","soundcloud.com/levisiteuronline"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Resident Advisor (RA)', 'magazine', 'paid', 'web', '{"house","tech house","techno","electronic"}', 'form', 'feedback@ra.co', 'RA account login required for the feature pitch form. For release reviews: pitch via feedback@ra.co specifying which release and why it is noteworthy. For feature pitches: use ra.co/pitch/feature with a 4 to 5 sentence explanation of the artist/topic''s relevance. Long-form features, release reviews, opinion pieces, and video essays accepted feedback@ra.co confirmed on ra.co/about/contribute for review pitches. Feature form at ra.co/pitch/feature requires login. RA is highly selective and skews toward established acts for main features; singles reviews and Breaking Through series are more realistic for unknowns. Active open to pitches as of April 2025.', '8M+ monthly unique visitors; definitive global underground electronic music authority', 'The world''s leading electronic music magazine and event platform. RA singles reviews, features, and premieres carry enormous credibility globally. Open to pitches for release reviews and features from anyone. The ''Singles Reviews'' section and ''Breaking Through'' series are the most accessible entry points for unknown artists.', '{"ra.co/about/contribute","ra.co/pitch/feature"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('6AM Group', 'blog', 'freemium', 'web', '{"house","tech house","techno"}', 'email', 'services@6amgroup.com', 'High-quality original house or techno track. Allow at least 2 weeks for completion. Paid service: Basic Premiere $49 (SoundCloud upload only), Standard Premiere $99 (SoundCloud + site post + social), Press/Editorial Feature $39 PAID promo service — not free editorial. services@6amgroup.com confirmed on official services page. No refunds per their terms. Contact form on About page also available for organic inquiries. Flagged: budget required.', 'Large social following; active Discord community; established underground audience', 'US-based underground electronic media platform featuring premieres, interviews, guest mixes, and editorial coverage of house and techno. Content-promo service routes tracks to their editorial team and SoundCloud channel. Paid tier makes placement predictable with a modest budget.', '{"6amgroup.com/services/content-promo","6amgroup.com/about"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('House Music With Love (HMWL)', 'blog', 'free', 'web', '{"deep house","afro house","organic house","melodic house","melodic techno"}', 'form', 'https://www.housemusicwithlove.com/submit-a-hmwl-premiere-or-upload/', 'SoundCloud or Dropbox link only. Specify release date for premiere requests. Must fit: Afro House, Organic House, Deep House, Melodic House & Techno, or Electronica Embedded web form on official submission page — no email listed. Confirmed active with HMWL Podcasts 2025 playlist on SoundCloud. Also runs HMWL Records label imprints. Pure tech house without melodic/organic elements may not fit their aesthetic.', 'Claims 12M+ followers across channels; active Spotify playlists and SoundCloud', 'Swedish house music blog, record label, and repost network active since 2008. Offers blog reviews, YouTube/SoundCloud premieres, and Spotify playlist placements to a self-described 12M+ follower audience. An accessible launch platform for deep/melodic house and organic house tracks from completely unknown artists.', '{"housemusicwithlove.com/submit-a-hmwl-premiere-or-upload","soundcloud.com/hmwl/sets/hmwl-podcasts-2025"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('This Song Is Sick', 'blog', 'free', 'web', '{"electronic","house","deep house","dance","indie"}', 'portal', 'https://www.submithub.com/blog/thissongissick-com', 'Submit via SubmitHub only — no direct email accepted. Electronic, house, indie, hip-hop accepted SubmitHub is the only submission channel, confirmed on thissongissick.com. Site active with premieres through May 2025. Broader editorial focus — house tracks with a strong hook or distinctive identity will stand out.', 'Global readership in 110+ countries; long-running social presence', 'Established US music discovery blog active since 2010 with a dedicated premieres section and global readership in 110+ countries. Covers electronic, house, and dance music alongside indie and hip-hop. Most recent premiere confirmed May 2025. SubmitHub submission is open to all artists.', '{"thissongissick.com","thissongissick.com/section/premieres"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('We Rave You', 'blog', 'free', 'web', '{"house","tech house","techno","electronic"}', 'form', 'general@weraveyou.com', 'Artist name. Email address. Track URL. Brief message describing the track and request Artist submission form confirmed on official contact page. general@weraveyou.com also active. They claim 5-hour response time and assign a specialist. Active House & Techno Picks series confirmed as of June 2025.', '35M+ monthly content reach; 1M+ followers', 'Large-scale electronic music media brand with 35M+ monthly content reach and 1M+ followers. Runs a recurring ''House & Techno Picks'' editorial series (confirmed June 2025) showcasing independent artists. Artist submission form on contact page assigns a dedicated consultant per submission.', '{"weraveyou.com/contact","weraveyou.com/2025/06/we-rave-you-presents-house-techno-picks-featuring-daijo-ward-andrews-more"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Spotify for Artists — Editorial Pitch', 'playlist_curator', 'free', 'Spotify', '{"house","tech house","electronic"}', 'portal', 'https://artists.spotify.com', 'Music must be distributed to Spotify via any distributor. Must pitch at least 7 days before release date (28 days strongly recommended for unknowns). Only unreleased tracks eligible — pitch disappears once track is live. One track pitch per release; cannot pitch compilations or featured-artist slots. Complete pitch form: genre, mood, instruments, 500-character story about the song. Artist profile must be complete — bio, press photo, linked socials Completely free. No middleman. After release, eligible artists can pin the pitched song to their ''This Is'' playlist for up to 28 days. Placement is not guaranteed; editorial team selects roughly 1-in-5 pitched tracks industry-wide.', 'Editorial playlists range from thousands to millions of followers; Release Radar reaches every artist follower', 'The only official, free route to Spotify''s in-house editorial team. A placement on a Spotify editorial playlist (e.g. ''Mint'', ''Dance Brandneu'') can deliver tens of thousands of streams overnight and kick-start the algorithm for an unknown artist.', '{"support.spotify.com/us/artists/article/pitching-music-to-playlist-editors","chartlex.com/blog/streaming/spotify-playlist-pitching-guide-2025"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('SubmitHub — Playlist Curator Network', 'playlist_curator', 'freemium', 'Spotify / SoundCloud / Apple Music', '{"house","tech house","techno","electronic"}', 'portal', 'https://www.submithub.com', 'Create a free artist account on submithub.com. Upload or link Spotify/SoundCloud track. Filter curators by genre (techno-house, deep tech, electronic). Write a 200-character pitch for each submission. Free submissions: curators have 20 days to respond, no feedback obligation. Premium credits ($0.79–$3 each, bulk discounts): 48-hr response + written feedback guaranteed PAID for premium tier. 10 credits = $10; 100 credits = $80. Platform-wide approval rate ~5–8% for premium. Tech house / electronic genres see 8–12% approval rates, which is above average. Free tier response rate has dropped to under 10%. Over 4.5 million submissions processed in 2025.', '6,000+ active curators; individual playlists range from 1K to 500K+ followers', 'Largest curator marketplace with 6,000+ active curators. Has a dedicated tech house / techno-house filter, making it one of the most targeted discovery tools for an unknown house producer. Free tier available; paid tier guarantees 48-hr feedback.', '{"submithub.com/playlister/techno-house","musicpulse.app/blog/is-submithub-still-worth-it-in-2026-an-honest-review","loopsolitaire.co.uk/blog/how-to-use-submithub-2025"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Groover — House & Tech House Curators', 'playlist_curator', 'paid', 'Spotify / SoundCloud / other', '{"house","tech house","afro house","deep house","melodic house"}', 'portal', 'https://groover.co/en/influencer/list/tags/tech-house/playlist/', 'Create a Groover account at groover.co. Purchase Grooviz credits (€46 starter pack = 46 Grooviz; bulk saves up to 24%). Each curator contact costs 2 Grooviz (~€2); premium curators 4–6 Grooviz. Select curators filtered by ''tech-house'' or ''house music'' tags. Submit track link and write a short pitch. Response guaranteed within 7 days — refund issued if curator fails to respond PAID. Standard rate: ~€2 per curator contact. Most successful campaigns contact 50+ curators (€100+ investment). Credits never expire. Average answer rate >85%. Top-tier curators on the platform include playlist channels, radio hosts, and label A&Rs who review the same submission.', '141+ house-tagged curators; 76+ tech-house-tagged curators; individual contacts vary from micro-playlists to 100K+ follower channels', 'Paris-based platform with 4,000+ music pros. Has an explicit tech-house curator filter and a dedicated ''HOUSE 2025 | Tech House & Club Music'' Spotify-certified playlist. Every submission is guaranteed a written reply within 7 days or credits are refunded — de-risks spending for an unknown artist.', '{"groover.co/en/influencer/profile/0.house-2023-tech-house-club-music","groover.co/en/lp/pricing","groover.co/en"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Playlist Push — Spotify Curator Campaigns', 'playlist_curator', 'paid', 'Spotify', '{"house","tech house","electronic","EDM"}', 'portal', 'https://playlistpush.com', 'Create account at playlistpush.com. Submit track details: Spotify link, genre, mood, language, release date, short description. Select campaign size — minimum $285 for Spotify campaigns. Pre-release campaigns available up to 14 days before drop date. Track must be on Spotify (released or scheduled) PAID. Campaigns start at $285; average is $400–$450; large campaigns can exceed $1,000. Pricing scales with number of curator matches. $285 campaign may yield ~500–3,000 streams over 30 days. $450 campaign: ~2,000–8,000 streams. Electronic and house genres have high curator density, which can push pricing up slightly. 45,000+ artists have used the platform.', '1,000+ curators; total combined reach ~23 million Spotify listeners', 'Vetted network of 1,000+ independent Spotify playlist curators with verified organic engagement. Campaigns run for two weeks, matching the track to genre-relevant curators. Pre-release campaigns can drive saves/streams in the critical first 48 hours of release — very important for Spotify''s algorithm.', '{"playlistpush.com/pricing","playlistpush.com","chartlex.com/blog/streaming/playlist-push-review-2026"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Soundplate — House / Electronic Playlist Submission', 'playlist_curator', 'freemium', 'Spotify', '{"house","tech house","deep house","electronic","dance"}', 'form', 'https://soundplate.com/new-spotify-playlists1/electronic-dance/', 'Browse curated playlists at soundplate.com/new-spotify-playlists1/electronic-dance/. Listen to playlists first to confirm genre fit. Click ''Submit Music'' on chosen playlist page. Sign in with Spotify to submit (platform auto-follows the playlist). Submit one track at a time — quality over quantity Completely FREE. Soundplate also runs its own ''Official Soundplate'' playlists updated with hot electronic tracks — submit at soundplate.com/new-spotify-playlists1/official-soundplate-playlists/. Additional free tools available: pre-save campaigns, Spotify track analyzer, playlist analyzer.', 'Hundreds of independent Spotify curators on platform; individual playlists range from 500 to 100K+ followers', 'Free platform dedicated to connecting electronic / house music artists with independent Spotify curators. Has a specific ''House / Electronic / Dance Music'' submission section with dozens of curators. No account needed for basic discovery; Spotify login required to submit. Ideal low-barrier starting point for an unknown artist with no budget.', '{"soundplate.com/new-spotify-playlists1/electronic-dance","soundplate.com/submit-music-spotify-playlists","soundplate.com/15-dance-music-spotify-curators-submit-your-music-free"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Daily Playlists — Spotify Curator Marketplace', 'playlist_curator', 'freemium', 'Spotify', '{"house","tech house","techno","electronic","dance"}', 'portal', 'https://dailyplaylists.com/submit-song/add-song', 'Create free account at dailyplaylists.com. Connect Spotify account via Spotify authenticator. Search/paste Spotify track URL. Filter playlists by genre (house, tech house, electronic). Use 20 free Standard credits per week (reset every Monday). Premium credits available for purchase for larger campaigns FREE tier: 20 credits/week, no charge. Premium credits available for paid campaigns. Platform has facilitated over 7 million playlist placements since 2017 launch. Curators include active playlists with 50K–190K+ followers specifically in house/tech house (e.g. ''Techno House Top #1 Hits'' 190K followers; ''★ HOUSE 2025 ★'' 114K followers; ''TECH HOUSE MAFIA 2025'' 159K followers).', '18,000+ playlists; 40,000+ curators; top house playlists on platform: 60K–190K followers', 'One of the largest free playlist submission networks (18,000+ playlists, 40,000+ curators). Hands out 20 free Standard credits per week per artist — meaning an unknown producer can start submitting at zero cost. Has a dedicated house genre filter and actively lists curated top-10 house playlists available for free submission.', '{"dailyplaylists.com/en/blog/spotify-top-10-free-house-playlists-2025","dailyplaylists.com/blog/submit-music-spotify-playlists-independent-curators-guide"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('SoundCampaign (SoundCamps) — Spotify Curator Matching', 'playlist_curator', 'paid', 'Spotify', '{"house","tech house","electronic"}', 'portal', 'https://soundcamps.com', 'Create account at soundcamps.com. Set a campaign budget (no minimum stated; ~£150 to reach ~21 curators typical). Select genre and sub-genre to narrow curator matching. Platform auto-matches and distributes track to curators. Only pay when curator reviews the submission or a TikTok video is delivered PAID. Budget-flexible — you set the spending cap. Typical campaign: ~£150 for 21 curators; ~10–20% add your track to a playlist. Curators are paid per review, driving accountability. Real campaign example: $300 budget, 21 curators, 5 playlist adds, 4,223 streams. No monthly fee.', 'Curated network of verified Spotify playlist curators; typical campaign reaches 15–50 curators', 'Transparent, budget-controlled platform that auto-matches tracks to Spotify playlist curators and only charges when submissions are reviewed. Sub-genre selection available, so a house/tech house producer can narrow targeting. Curators are compensated for reviews, which keeps response rates high. Good secondary platform to diversify beyond SubmitHub and Groover.', '{"soundcamps.com","melodicmind.co/soundcampaign-review","skopemag.com/2025/08/18/which-one-is-the-best-music-promotion-platforms-submithub-one-submit-playlist-push-and-soundcampaign"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('One Submit — Spotify Playlist & Blog Promotion', 'playlist_curator', 'paid', 'Spotify', '{"house","tech house","electronic","techno"}', 'portal', 'https://www.one-submit.com/spotify-promotion', 'Create account at one-submit.com. Select Spotify track link. Choose playlist size tier: up to 8K followers = $3; 8K–20K = $6 per submission. Each campaign runs for 10 days. Refund issued if curator does not respond within 10 days PAID. Per-submission pricing scaled by playlist size. Guarantees written feedback from curators. Described as ''much cheaper than Playlist Push'' by platform. Supports multiple genres; curators include house, tech house, afro house channels. Also offers music blog and TikTok influencer submissions on same platform.', '2,200+ curators on platform; individual playlist curators range from 1K to 100K+ followers', 'Pay-per-submission platform with 2,200+ Spotify playlist curators. Artists choose playlists by follower size and only pay for what they target. Has a tech-house-to-Afro-house cross-genre submission route verified on the site (''Submit Tech House to Afrohouse Chill Sunset''). Ranked best Spotify promotion service by several music industry outlets in 2025.', '{"one-submit.com/curator/submit-tech-house-to-afrohouse-chill-sunset-spotify-promotion","one-submit.com/spotify-promotion","skopemag.com/2025/08/18/which-one-is-the-best-music-promotion-platforms-submithub-one-submit-playlist-push-and-soundcampaign"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Electronic Radar — House & Tech House Submission', 'playlist_curator', 'free', 'Spotify', '{"house","tech house","deep tech","techno","afro house","jackin house"}', 'email', 'info@electronicradar.com', 'Send Spotify link only (no other platform links). Track must be released in 2025 or 2026 (current year). Electronic music genres only — house, tech house, techno and subgenres. Free submission — no charge FREE. Accepted tracks are first placed on ''Electronic Radar Last Submissions'' playlist, then considered for main genre playlists. Curator self-describes as ''small but with big things in mind''. Also active on Mixcloud, Instagram, YouTube, and SoundCloud. Great for early traction with a genre-focused audience.', '17 curated Spotify playlists; overall scale is small/emerging but genre-targeted', 'Small but genre-focused independent curator running 17 Spotify playlists specifically for techno and house subgenres including ''House Radar'', ''Tech House Radar'', ''Deep Tech'', ''Jackin House'', ''Afro Energy''. Accepts free email submissions from any indie artist with a 2025 Spotify release — exactly the kind of niche, accessible outlet an unknown artist needs.', '{"electronicradar.com/submit-music"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Indiemono — Pop / EDM & Chill Playlist Submission', 'playlist_curator', 'freemium', 'Spotify / Deezer / Apple Music', '{"electronic","house (chill)","deep house","dance","EDM"}', 'form', 'https://indiemono.com/music-submit/', 'Submit via form at indiemono.com/music-submit/. Choose the genre box that best fits your track (Pop/EDM or Chill for house music). Submit once — Indiemono routes internally across multiple playlists. Track to Spotify for Artists to monitor placement Completely FREE. No individual feedback provided due to volume. Indiemono explicitly states: ''We don''t sell placements and won''t accept transactions to be included in any playlist.'' House/tech house may not fit all their boxes; best fit is Chill or Pop/EDM categories. Also manages an ''EDM Remixes, Phonk & House 2025'' Spotify playlist. Demo submission available for unreleased tracks.', '100+ playlists; 3M+ combined playlist followers across Spotify, Deezer, and Apple Music', 'Free, editorial submission system across 100+ curated playlists with 3M+ playlist followers. Covers Chill Deep House and Dance/EDM categories that intersect with house music. Submission is free, editorial, and requires zero marketing spend — a safe no-cost channel for any unknown artist to attempt.', '{"indiemono.com/music-submit","indiemono.com","open.spotify.com/playlist/5MA2NuCMiDEdV6edU5GpO7"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Tech Me Home — House & Techno Promotion', 'playlist_curator', 'freemium', 'Spotify / DJ platforms', '{"house","tech house","techno","afro house","minimal","melodic house"}', 'form', 'contact@techmehomechannel.com', 'Complete submission form at techmehomechannel.com/submit-your-song. House, techno, and underground electronic music only. Response within 48 hours (up to 72 hours during busy periods) Pricing not publicly listed on the submission page — expect a paid service based on service scope (Inflyte DJ campaigns, Spotify playlisting, press campaigns are professional services). Free initial submission inquiry via form. Response time guaranteed within 48 hrs. Also offers Hypeddit free-download campaigns.', 'Network of DJs, radio hosts and producers on Inflyte; curated Spotify playlists for house/techno audience', 'Dedicated house/techno promotion service offering Spotify playlisting, Inflyte DJ campaigns, and press services. Minimum 28-day playlist placement per track. Specialist in underground electronic genres with direct DJ outreach — useful for an artist trying to get tracks into professional DJ sets as well as playlists.', '{"techmehomechannel.com/submit-your-song","techmehomechannel.com"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Apple Music Pitch (via Distributor / Apple Music Connect)', 'playlist_curator', 'freemium', 'Apple Music', '{"house","tech house","electronic"}', 'portal', 'https://musicconnect.apple.com/support/5575-apple-music-pitch', 'Music distributed to Apple Music via a distributor partner with Apple Music Connect access. Pitch submitted by distributor at least 10 days before release (7-day minimum for late adds). Provide: content format, track name, mood, genre, language, release date, campaign details. Note any focus/feeler track if part of an EP or album. Artist biography not required — campaign context is more important FREE (built into distributor workflow). Independent artists cannot pitch directly — must go through their distributor. Check with your distributor (TuneCore, DistroKid, CD Baby, Amuse etc.) whether they offer Apple Music Pitch as part of release setup. Organic buzz and placement on user-generated playlists can also attract editorial attention independently.', 'Apple Music editorial playlists can reach millions of subscribers globally; ''A-List: Electronic'' is a top-tier flagship playlist', 'Apple Music''s editorial team curates high-profile playlists (e.g. ''A-List: Electronic''). While direct access is restricted to distributor partners, many indie distributors (TuneCore, DistroKid, Amuse, CD Baby) now offer Apple Music editorial pitching as part of their release flow — making this accessible to a solo artist with any reputable distributor.', '{"musicconnect.apple.com/support/5575-apple-music-pitch","playlistpush.com/blog/how-to-get-on-apple-music-playlists-a-guide-for-independent-artists","imusician.pro/en/products/editorial-playlist-pitching"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('MusoSoup — Music Promotion Marketplace', 'playlist_curator', 'freemium', 'Spotify / blogs / social', '{"electronic","house","indie electronic"}', 'portal', 'https://musosoup.com/', 'Create artist account at musosoup.com. Pay one-off campaign fee from £42. Upload release details (up to 90 days before release date). Curators browse and send offers — accept or decline paid/free coverage. No ongoing subscription needed PAID one-off fee (from £42 per campaign). Curators on platform are independent bloggers, playlist curators, radio stations, and social creators. House/electronic music coverage depends on which curators are active on the platform at time of submission — genre coverage is broader indie-electronic than specialist underground house. Good supplementary channel for press + playlist combo.', 'Hundreds of verified curators; covers Spotify playlists, blogs, radio, and social features across multiple genres', 'Unique reverse-pitch model: curators browse and contact artists they like, rather than artists cold-pitching. A single one-off fee gives 90 days of visibility to the curator pool. Covers Spotify playlists, blog reviews, radio airplay, and social media features — broader than playlist-only platforms.', '{"musosoup.com","musosoup.com/artists-how-it-works","twostorymelody.com/musosoup-review"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Beatport / Beatportal — Editorial Pitching for DJ Store', 'playlist_curator', 'free', 'Beatport', '{"house","tech house","techno","deep house"}', 'none-public', 'https://greenroom.beatport.com/artists', 'Distribute to Beatport via TuneCore, DistroKid, or MusicHub (no label required). Pitch for editorial features through your distributor''s label manager contact at Beatport. Pitch 3–4 weeks before release for full editorial consideration. Can enter remix contests via LabelRadar (free). Apply annually for Beatport Next artist development program. Social Spotlight (Drop of the Week, Studio Jam) can be pitched via Beatport''s social channels Distribution is standard-cost via distributor. Editorial pitching itself is free but must go via distributor label manager. Beatport Hype chart ranks emerging artists specifically — getting into Hype Top 100 for Tech House is a significant credibility signal. No direct artist-to-editorial email publicly listed.', 'Millions of DJs and electronic music fans globally; Tech House Top 100 and Hype charts are watched by working DJs worldwide', 'Beatport is the #1 download store for DJs and the definitive platform for house/tech-house discovery by professional DJs. Editorial features on Beatportal (Artist of Month, Playlist of Week, track breakdowns) directly influence DJ chart picks and festival bookings. Beatport Hype chart is specifically for emerging artists. Independent artists can distribute to Beatport without a label via TuneCore, DistroKid, or MusicHub.', '{"greenroom.beatport.com/artists","beatport.com/genre/tech-house/11/hype-100"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Deeper Shades of House', 'podcast', 'paid', 'Mixcloud / SoundCloud / web', '{"deep house","afro house","house"}', 'email', 'lars@deepershades.net', 'Contact Lars first via the site form with links to recent mixes and a bio before sending the full mix. Mix must be EXCLUSIVE — not broadcast or uploaded elsewhere before or after. WAV, AIFF, or 320kbps MP3 minimum; minimum 60 minutes. At least 4dB headroom (do not peak at 0dB). No AI-produced music in the mix. No voiceovers, jingles, or station IDs. Full tracklist in format: Artist – Title (Remix) – Label. Short bio, social/website links, two high-quality photos. File named: DJName-MixTitle.mp3 with ID3 tags Paid: No. Guest mixes are unpaid exposure. High submission volume; Lars personally reviews.', '500k+ podcast subscribers; 140k+ Mixcloud followers', 'Long-running weekly podcast (900+ episodes) hosted by Lars Behrenroth; actively invites guest mixes from lesser-known producers via a public submission page — one of the few major house podcasts with an explicit open-submission policy for unknowns.', '{"deepershades.net/submit-a-guest-mix.html"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('When We Dip – Prima Lux Mix Series', 'podcast', 'paid', 'SoundCloud / web / Spotify', '{"melodic house","deep house","house"}', 'email', 'promo@whenwedip.com', 'Submit mix link (SoundCloud/streaming) and bio. Relevant to deep/melodic house spectrum. Original, exclusive or premiere-quality mix preferred Prima Lux series is specifically designed for emerging artists. Contact form also at whenwedip.com/contact-us/. Paid: No.', 'Magazine readership 50k+; active global social following; SoundCloud Prima Lux playlist 5k+ followers', 'Active dance music magazine (Montreal/Dublin/Berlin) running the ''Prima Lux'' dedicated emerging-artist mix series — episodes published as recently as May 2026, confirming the series actively curates lesser-known DJs. The main When We Dip Mix series (episodes 170-188+ in 2025-2026) runs in parallel for more established names.', '{"whenwedip.com/podcasts/prima-lux","new.whenwedip.com/2026/05/prima-lux-sideral"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('6AM Group (SIX AM) – Guest Mix Series', 'podcast', 'paid', 'web / SoundCloud / YouTube', '{"house","tech house","techno","electronic"}', 'form', 'https://6amgroup.com/about', 'Submit inquiry via the contact form on the About page at 6amgroup.com/about. Include mix link, bio, and social media profiles. Mix should showcase a unique sound No dedicated submission email found on the site; editorial contact via the web form. Instagram DM @6amgroup also a viable approach. Paid: No for editorial placement.', 'Major US EDM media platform; 100k+ social followers across channels', 'Weekly guest mix series on a major US electronic music media platform; features a wide range of emerging artists (Nikka Lorak, Konrad James, DJ Nikadeemas, Angel Parilli) alongside established names — accessible to unknowns willing to pitch via contact form or social DM.', '{"6amgroup.com/articles/music-guest-mixes","6amgroup.com/about"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Proton Radio – Bedroom Bedlam / Guest Mix', 'podcast', 'paid', 'web / SoundCloud / Spotify', '{"house","tech house","progressive house","techno","minimal"}', 'email', 'demos@protonradio.com', 'Private SoundCloud link to your mix with downloads enabled. Tracklist formatted as: 01. Artist - Track (Mix) [Label]. Send to demos@protonradio.com Alternative path: contact existing Proton residents via SoundCloud to request a guest slot on their show. Label-distributed artists: support@protonradio.com. Paid: No.', 'Global underground EDM audience; 200+ shows; 50k+ SoundCloud followers', 'Long-standing internet radio station dedicated to underground dance music with 200+ shows; ''Bedroom Bedlam'' is an open-submission vehicle specifically designed to introduce lesser-known talent; successful demos can lead to ongoing residencies. Active tech house genre page confirmed 2025.', '{"intercom.help/proton-radio/en/articles/2872691-how-do-i-get-a-mix-or-radio-show-on-proton","protonradio.com/genres/2/tech-house"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Frisky Radio – Feelin'' Frisky Broadcasts', 'podcast', 'paid', 'web / frisky.fm', '{"house","deep house","progressive house","techno"}', 'email', 'submit@friskyradio.com', 'Email submit@friskyradio.com with a WeTansfer or streaming link in the email body. Include name, email, genre of the mix, and a brief bio. MP3 only — no WAV files, no email attachments. Do not contact via social media — email only. No guaranteed reply — only hear back if selected Heavily curated. Successful mixes can lead to a full recurring residency. Paid: No.', 'Specialist underground radio audience; active since 2000; 30k+ social following', 'Underground electronic music radio station with a curated 1-hour guest mix slot (''Feelin'' Frisky'') explicitly open to unsolicited submissions from DJs — one of the clearest open-door submission paths in the underground electronic space.', '{"friskyradio.com/show/feelin_frisky","frisky.fm/about"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Data Transmission – Spotlight Mix Series', 'podcast', 'paid', 'SoundCloud / web / Mixcloud', '{"house","tech house","deep tech","techno"}', 'email', 'grahame@datatransmission.co', 'Email Grahame Farmer (Editor-in-Chief) at grahame@datatransmission.co. Specify genre (house, tech house, deep tech, or techno). Include streaming link to your mix and an artist bio. Longer interview/feature pitches also accepted separately Paid repost service also exists separately at datatransmission.co/submit-your-repost/. Editorial spotlight mixes are unpaid. Paid: No for editorial mix slot.', 'Major dance music media site; 50k+ SoundCloud followers; global readership', 'Established online dance music authority with a regularly updated Spotlight Mix Series (active through Sept 2025) featuring artists from emerging to established; editorial contact is public and directly accessible to independent artists.', '{"datatransmission.co/contact","1001tracklists.com/tracklist/btr0p6k/channe-data-transmission-spotlight-mix-2025-09-17.html"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Magnetic Magazine – Guest Podcast Series', 'podcast', 'paid', 'SoundCloud / web', '{"house","tech house","techno","electronic"}', 'email', 'info@magneticmag.com', 'Submit a streaming link to your mix (no MP3 attachments). Include full contact details. Fresh, original-angle pitches preferred. Editorial team curates — not all submissions published Also accepts track premieres and artist features via same email. Content is editorially selected. Paid: No.', 'Global EDM readership 100k+; 200k+ social following', 'US-based electronic music magazine (Beverly Hills) with an established guest podcast series; submission policy is publicly documented and allows emerging artist pitches via email with a streaming link — no attachment required.', '{"magneticmag.com/submission-policy","magneticmag.com/tag/podcast"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('NTS Radio – Supporter Radio Mix Programme', 'podcast', 'paid', 'web / nts.live / Spotify', '{"house","techno","electronic","experimental"}', 'form', 'https://www.nts.live/projects/supporter-radio', 'Must be an NTS Supporter (membership from £3.99/month or ~£54/year). Watch for submission window announcements via newsletter and @nts_radio Instagram. Mix strictly 55–60 minutes long, submitted as an MP3. No genre restrictions — any electronic style welcome. Only one mix per applicant selected if multiple submitted Paid: Yes — NTS Supporter membership required (from £3.99/month). Submissions are evaluated by the programming team; no individual feedback for rejected mixes. 3–4 submission rounds per year. Next round reportedly opening summer 2026.', 'Global audience; NTS streams to 6M+ listeners per month; archived mixes remain on site', 'London-based broadcaster NTS opens a mix-submission programme several times per year exclusively to its supporters (paying members); selected mixes broadcast live and archived alongside resident programming — a legitimate, structured route for an unknown to get a mix on a globally respected radio platform.', '{"nts.live/projects/supporter-radio","ntslive.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/77000570080-submitting-a-mix","nts.live/supporters"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Electronic Groove – EG Podcast', 'podcast', 'paid', 'Mixcloud / SoundCloud / web / Apple Podcasts', '{"house","tech house","techno","progressive house","deep house"}', 'email', 'contact@electronicgroove.com', 'Email contact@electronicgroove.com with a streaming link to your mix and artist bio. Note your pitch is for the EG Podcast guest slot. No dedicated submission form — general contact email used for editorial pitches Note: Electronic Groove also offers paid track premiere packages ($40–$80) at electronicgroove.com/submission/ — these are separate from editorial podcast features. Paid: No for editorial podcast slot.', '1072+ episodes; Mixcloud followers 30k+; Apple Podcasts listed; global electronic music readership', 'Long-running electronic music magazine podcast (1072+ episodes as of June 2026) that regularly features both established and emerging artists (e.g. Diass, Lannka, Adapter, Charles Meyer alongside Steve Lawler, Cattáneo); general contact email accepted for guest mix pitches.', '{"electronicgroove.com/series/eg-podcast","electronicgroove.com/submission"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('MIL-MGMT (Music Is Love Management)', 'pr', 'paid', 'web', '{"house","tech house","techno","electronic"}', 'form', 'info@mil-mgmt.com', 'Submit private link or download of track(s). Provide release date, label and catalog details, and campaign objectives. Submit at least 6 weeks before release date. Select and pay for campaign tier via website checkout PAID service. Pricing: DJ Only £110 (EP)/£220 (Album); DJ+Radio £160/£265; Full Campaign (DJ+Radio+Press) £295.99–£449.99 for 6-week EP or 12-week Album campaigns. Use code ''decade'' for 10% off. Includes weekly reporting and real-time DJ feedback.', 'Network of DJs, specialist radio shows, press outlets, and playlist curators in house/techno space', 'Manchester-based PR firm with 10+ years specialising exclusively in house, techno and electronic music; offers tiered campaigns (DJ promo, radio plugging, press coverage) designed for independent artists and labels — the most accessible entry-level pricing in the sector (£110 for DJ-only EP campaign).', '{"mil-mgmt.com/house-music-pr","mil-mgmt.com/contact"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Reach Promo', 'pr', 'paid', 'web', '{"deep house","tech house","techno","minimal"}', 'email', 'info@reach-promo.agency', 'Email info@reach-promo.agency to check if music fits their service. Music must fit deep house / tech house / techno/minimal genres. Submit private streaming link for review before purchasing campaign PAID service. Pricing: Basic Campaign €80 (30 days, DJ outreach only, up to 2 tracks); Medium Campaign €100 (30 days, DJs+magazines+radio+3 news items, up to 2 tracks). Upfront payment required. Previous clients include Carl Cox, Spektre, Thomas Schumacher. Labels: Terminal M, Elevate, Trax Records, Tronic.', 'Curated pool of DJs, radio shows, and blogs in deep house/tech house/techno scene globally', 'Italy-based specialist PR agency and promo pool focused exclusively on deep house, tech house, and techno/minimal; affordable tiered campaigns (from €80) covering DJ outreach, radio promotion, blog/magazine pitching, and Spotify playlist submission — lowest entry cost among verified house-specific PR agencies.', '{"reach-promo.agency/promo-pool-services","reach-promo.agency/promo-pr-agency-promo-pool"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Infectious PR', 'pr', 'paid', 'web', '{"dance","electronic","house","pop"}', 'email', 'newbiz@infectiouspr.com', 'Email newbiz@infectiouspr.com with artist info and a streaming link to your music. Briefly describe your project and campaign goals PAID service — rates quoted on inquiry. UK-based, international reach. Team selects projects based on artistic fit (''Do we like it?''). Genre scope is broad dance/electronic.', 'Global media network; BBC, Forbes, Billboard, Apple Music, Spotify coverage capacity', 'Bristol-based marketing and PR agency (founded 2009, 30 years combined experience) with global media network including BBC, Forbes, Billboard, Apple Music, and Spotify; explicitly invites new project inquiries from emerging artists via their public new-business email.', '{"infectiouspr.com"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Motormouthmedia', 'pr', 'paid', 'web', '{"electronic","indie electronic","underground dance"}', 'email', 'submissions@motormouthmedia.com', 'Email submissions@motormouthmedia.com with project info and a streaming link. High submission volume — no reply indicates project is not a fit PAID service — rates quoted on inquiry. Selective boutique firm; evaluates based on artistic quality. Best fit for leftfield or underground electronic artists rather than mainstream commercial house.', 'US and international indie/electronic tastemaker press; established booking and label contacts', 'LA/Brooklyn boutique PR firm (founded late 1990s) that has championed underground electronic acts since the beginning — was the first American independent PR firm to represent Warp Records, Ninja Tune, Planet Mu; broke Four Tet, Caribou, Flying Lotus from day one; accepts new inquiries.', '{"motormouthmedia.com/contact","motormouthmedia.com/about"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Dispersion PR', 'pr', 'paid', 'web', '{"house","tech house","techno","electronic"}', 'email', 'info@dispersionpr.com', 'Email info@dispersionpr.com with artist/release info. Include streaming link and campaign goals. Specify release date and label context PAID service — rates quoted on inquiry. One of the most connected UK underground electronic music PR agencies. BBC Radio 1 Dance placement track record.', 'UK and European press, radio, and club circuit; BBC Radio 1 Dance history', 'UK specialist electronic music PR firm (founded 2007 by Julian Shay and Dean Muhsin) offering press, radio, and club promo for artists and labels. Client history includes Hot Creations, Crosstown Rebels, Cocoon, Defected, Laurent Garnier, Michael Bibi, Chris Liebing — working with Dispersion signals credibility in the underground house/techno circuit.', '{"dispersionpr.com","rocketreach.co/dispersion-pr-profile_b5d36282f42e46a9"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('MCPR (Matt Caldwell PR)', 'pr', 'paid', 'web', '{"electronic","house","techno","dance"}', 'email', 'info@mattcaldwell.co.uk', 'Email info@mattcaldwell.co.uk or use the contact form at mattcaldwell.co.uk/contact/. Include project details, streaming link, and campaign scope PAID service — rates quoted on inquiry. London-based (Covent Garden). Phone: +44 800 689 4723. Integrated services beyond PR include social media, creative, brand partnerships, radio.', 'International electronic music press, radio, and industry network; 12+ years established', 'Full-service 360-degree electronic music agency (12+ years, global presence) offering PR, radio promo, social media, A&R consultancy, and artist progression — contact email and phone publicly listed; targets both emerging and established electronic artists.', '{"mattcaldwell.co.uk/contact","mattcaldwell.co.uk"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Prescription Music PR', 'pr', 'paid', 'web', '{"electronic","ambient","house","dance"}', 'form', 'https://www.prescriptionmusicpruk.com/general-enquiries', 'Submit via the general enquiries form at prescriptionmusicpruk.com/general-enquiries. Include artist info, release details, and campaign objectives PAID service — pricing on inquiry. UK-based with European and Irish PR coverage. Phone: +44 (0)1223 505328 Mon–Fri 9am–6pm.', 'UK, European, and Irish music press and radio', 'Leading UK electronic and ambient music PR agency with offices in London, Cambridge, and Manchester; explicitly lists electronic music PR among services and has a public inquiry form for new campaign submissions — accessible to independent artists.', '{"prescriptionmusicpruk.com/electronic-music-pr","prescriptionmusicpruk.com/contact-us"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Groove Magazin – Resident Podcast', 'podcast', 'paid', 'SoundCloud / Mixcloud / web', '{"techno","house","electronic"}', 'email', 'max@groove.de', 'Email max@groove.de (Events/Podcast contact: Maximilian Fritz). Pitch yourself as a club resident or party organizer in a specific city/venue. Include streaming link to your mix and relevant club/party context. Note: primary focus is German-speaking regions and Eastern Europe — Tunis-based artists should pitch their regional/local residency angle if applicable Paid: No. Series is editorially curated and specifically oriented toward club residents in a defined geographic scope — an unknown Tunisian producer should pitch a specific residency or event angle rather than a generic mix. Low probability but possible if framed correctly.', 'Established German-language electronic music magazine; Mixcloud 50k+ followers; SoundCloud Resident Podcast playlist active', 'Berlin-based bi-monthly podcast (episode 064 published June 2026, confirming active status) featuring grassroots underground residents from clubs in German-speaking countries and Eastern Europe — focuses on local club culture figures rather than superstars. Podcast contact is publicly available via editorial email.', '{"groove.de/impressum","groove.de/category/podcast/groove-resident-podcast"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Rinse FM', 'radio', 'free', 'FM / web / SoundCloud', '{"house","tech house","dubstep","grime","electronica"}', 'email', 'thelinkup@rinse.fm', 'Private SoundCloud link only (no file attachments). Include brief artist bio and genre info Individual show hosts also run their own submission inboxes; contact show hosts directly via social for specific shows.', 'Online + 103.7 FM London; global streaming audience; tens of thousands weekly listeners', 'Rinse FM is the UK''s most influential underground radio station with 30+ years of history. Its shows are curated by individual DJs who actively seek fresh tracks — emailing thelinkup@rinse.fm with a private SoundCloud link is a direct route to DJ inboxes that spin house and tech house.', '{"labelsbase.net/rinse","rinse.fm"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Defected Radio', 'radio', 'free', 'web / Spotify / SoundCloud / podcast', '{"house","deep house","soulful house"}', 'portal', 'demos@defected.com', 'Streaming link with download option. Brief bio (1 paragraph). Social media links. No attachments — streaming link only. Track must be original, not a bootleg or mashup LabelRadar is the primary portal. demos@defected.com also accepted. Submission considered for all Defected sub-labels including Glitterbox, DFTD, D4 Dance.', '2M+ SoundCloud followers; Spotify editorial placement; syndicated to 70+ stations', 'Defected Radio is the world''s most-listened-to house music radio show, syndicated globally. Sending a promo to Defected''s demos portal (LabelRadar) is the official route to reaching their A&R and radio team — tracks featured can go on air and to their 2M+ SoundCloud followers.', '{"defected.com/demos","labelradar.com/labels/defected/portal","beatportal.com/articles/155155-defected-records-is-now-open-for-demo-submissions-via-labelradar"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Proton Radio — Bedroom Bedlam', 'radio', 'free', 'web / SoundCloud / Mixcloud', '{"house","tech house","deep house","progressive house","breaks","techno"}', 'email', 'demos@protonradio.com', 'Private SoundCloud link with downloads enabled. Tracklist formatted as: 01. Artist - Track (Mix) [Label]. Include artist bio and genre info Bedroom Bedlam airs on Proton Radio and accepts sets across electronic genres including house. Successful guest spots can lead to recurring invitations. Label-distributed artists can also contact support@protonradio.com.', '200+ exclusive shows; global internet radio audience; SoundCloud/Mixcloud archive', 'Proton Radio is one of the longest-running underground electronic internet radio networks with 200+ exclusive shows. ''Bedroom Bedlam'' is specifically the submission-friendly show that airs sets from emerging DJs — it is the documented front door for unknowns.', '{"intercom.help/proton-radio/en/articles/2872691-how-do-i-get-a-mix-or-radio-show-on-proton","protonradio.com/shows/321/bedroom-bedlam"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Frisky Radio — Feelin'' Frisky', 'radio', 'paid', 'web / SoundCloud / Mixcloud / podcast', '{"house","tech house","progressive house","deep house","techno"}', 'email', 'submit@friskyradio.com', 'MP3 only (no WAV). 320 kbps quality. Upload to WeTransfer — do NOT use SoundCloud, Mediafire or similar. Include: your name, email, genre of mix, and brief bio. Full 1-hour set required FRISKY uses a vetting process. Feelin'' Frisky broadcasts are limited 1-hour slots. Strong sets may lead to residency offers.', 'One of the largest underground electronic internet radio platforms; global audience; podcast distribution', 'Frisky Radio is a globally-streamed curated electronic music internet radio. ''Feelin'' Frisky'' is their dedicated guest slot for emerging DJs — it is the official, documented submission route for artists without an existing residency. A successful set can lead to a full residency offer.', '{"frisky.fm","friskyradio.com/about/faq"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Foundation FM', 'radio', 'free', 'web / SoundCloud / Mixcloud', '{"house","tech house","deep house","electronic","garage"}', 'email', 'ana@foundation.fm', 'Show/mix proposal describing your concept. SoundCloud or Mixcloud demo link recommended. Include artist bio and social links Show submissions go to ana@foundation.fm and angelica@foundation.fm. Creative/partnership enquiries go to beckytong@foundation.fm. General enquiries to hello@foundation.fm.', 'London-based online station with growing global listenership; active SoundCloud and Mixcloud presence', 'Foundation FM is a female-led independent London station championing underrepresented voices and emerging artists in underground electronic music. It actively curates new talent via a dedicated show submissions contact and has a track record of platforming unknowns.', '{"foundation.fm/info","soundcloud.com/foundation-fm"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('NTS Radio — Show Proposal / Supporter Radio', 'radio', 'freemium', 'web / SoundCloud / Mixcloud', '{"house","tech house","electronic","experimental","all genres"}', 'form', 'https://www.nts.live/contact', 'Show proposal: describe concept in up to 600 characters, list up to 5 genres, provide up to 3 demo links (SoundCloud/Mixcloud/YouTube). Supporter Radio: must be NTS Supporter (paid subscriber); 55–60 minute mix as MP3; submissions align with an announced theme Show proposal form at nts.live/contact. Supporter Radio rounds open a few times per year — follow @ntslive on Instagram for announcements. No direct submission email listed.', 'Millions of monthly listeners globally; 24/7 streaming; extensive archive', 'NTS is one of the world''s top independent online radio stations broadcasting 24/7. It has two documented entry routes for unknowns: (1) free show proposals via their website form, and (2) NTS Supporter Radio — a paid subscription scheme that opens mix submission rounds several times per year, with selected mixes broadcast and archived.', '{"ntslive.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/77000570099-show-proposals","nts.live/projects/supporter-radio","ntslive.freshdesk.com/support/solutions/articles/77000570080-submitting-a-mix"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Worldwide FM', 'radio', 'free', 'web / SoundCloud / Mixcloud', '{"house","deep house","soul","jazz","world","electronic"}', 'email', 'info@worldwidefm.net', 'Detailed show proposal: concept, planned guests for 6 months, specialty, genre focus, why it is original. Music submission via streaming link. Show must offer something distinct from existing programming Contact via email or website contact form. Station actively looks for shows highlighting underrepresented global scenes — a Tunisian/North African house perspective has strong pitch angle.', 'Global online audience; associated with Gilles Peterson''s worldwide network; Mixcloud archive', 'Worldwide FM (Gilles Peterson) champions underground and global music culture. Their contact page invites show proposals and music submissions. The station has a history of platforming emerging artists and international talent, making it realistic for a Tunisian producer to pitch a culturally distinctive show concept.', '{"worldwidefm.net/contact","worldwidefm.net/about"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Ibiza Live Radio — New Talent Show', 'radio', 'free', 'web / FM Ibiza', '{"house","deep house","tech house","electronic"}', 'form', 'https://www.ibizaliveradio.com/music/demo', 'Upload mix or demo track via upload portal at ibizaliveradio.affekt.de/upload-area. Include artist info and project description. Mix/set format preferred Monthly competition. Winning artist broadcast as guest on Ibiza Live Radio. Station covers house, electronic, deep, and tech genres.', 'Online + Ibiza FM; growing international listenership; active social media', 'Ibiza Live Radio runs a monthly ''New Talent Show'' competition specifically for unknown DJs and producers — the winning mix gets broadcast and the artist is featured as a guest. This is one of the most direct, documented routes for an unknown to get airplay on an Ibiza-branded station.', '{"ibizaliveradio.com/music/demo","ibizaliveradio.com"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Ibiza Global Radio', 'radio', 'free', 'FM / web / SoundCloud', '{"house","tech house","electronic","Ibiza club sounds"}', 'email', 'info@ibizaglobalradio.com', 'DJ mix or show proposal via email. Include artist bio, SoundCloud/streaming link. Specify genre and concept No dedicated submission portal found; general contact email is the documented contact route. Approach professionally with a mix link and brief pitch. Active as of 2025 (Ibiza Global Festival 2025 referenced).', '100.8 FM Ibiza + global web streaming; 186K+ Instagram followers; international syndication', 'Ibiza Global Radio is a 24/7 broadcast station (100.8 FM Ibiza) streaming the best international DJs and electronic music. Reaching them via their contact email is a real route to pitch DJ mix shows or promos to their programming team.', '{"ibizaglobalradio.com/contacts.html","ibizaglobalradio.com"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Passion Ibiza Radio', 'radio', 'free', 'web / Mixcloud / SoundCloud', '{"house","soulful house","disco","tech house","deep house","afro house","melodic house"}', 'form', 'https://passionibizaradio.com/submit-a-demo/', '60-minute pre-recorded show or continuous mix. MP3 at 320 kbps. SoundCloud download link. Include name, email, optional Facebook/Instagram links Response within a few days if accepted. Website notes limited show slots available. Form-based submission — no email address listed.', 'Online radio with Mixcloud/SoundCloud presence; Ibiza-focused audience; active as of June 2025', 'Passion Ibiza Radio has a fully open, documented demo submission form for emerging DJs — one of the most directly accessible Ibiza-branded stations. They actively seek quality house DJs and presenters and accept continuous mix submissions.', '{"passionibizaradio.com/submit-a-demo","mixcloud.com/passionibizaradio"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('BBC Introducing', 'radio', 'free', 'FM / BBC Radio 1 / BBC Radio 6 Music / web', '{"house","electronic","all genres (routed by region/genre)"}', 'portal', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/introducing', 'Create a free BBC account. Upload WAV or MP3 file (up to 2 tracks per upload cycle). Complete artist profile: name, genre, postcode, bio, photo (1920x1080px recommended). Upload clean version only — no explicit lyrics. Add PRS Tunecode if applicable Upload limit: 2 tracks every 30 days. Can take up to 6 months or more to be heard due to volume. Artists must be UK-based or have a UK postcode connection. Tracks routed to appropriate regional and national shows.', 'BBC Radio 1, Radio 6 Music, 1Xtra, 2, and regional stations; millions of listeners', 'BBC Introducing is the official BBC pathway for unsigned/emerging artists to reach BBC Radio 1, Radio 6 Music, 1Xtra, and regional BBC stations. Uploaded tracks are reviewed by producers and can be broadcast nationally. The upload portal is free and open to all UK-based or UK-connected artists. Dance/electronic tracks are routed to relevant shows including Radio 1 Dance.', '{"dittomusic.com/en/blog/how-to-get-your-music-played-on-bbc-introducing","en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BBC_Music_Introducing"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Netil Radio', 'radio', 'free', 'web / Mixcloud', '{"house","electronic","underground","experimental"}', 'email', 'hello@netilradio.com', 'Show proposal describing concept and music policy. Demo mix link (Mixcloud or SoundCloud). Artist bio and background Email hello@netilradio.com with show proposal. Station is community-led and actively curates new residents. Active as of 2025.', 'Online streaming; Mixcloud archive; London underground music community audience', 'Netil Radio is a Hackney community station broadcasting from a converted shipping container at Netil Market. It actively platforms emerging and underground artists and accepts show proposals via a documented email address. Its community-first ethos makes it more accessible than major stations.', '{"netilradio.com","streema.com/radios/Netil_Radio"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Toolroom Radio', 'radio', 'free', 'web / Mixcloud / podcast (Apple, Spotify)', '{"tech house","house","techno"}', 'portal', 'https://toolroomrecords.com/demos/', 'Upload demo via portal at toolroomrecords.com/demos/. Original productions only (not bootlegs). Label does not reply to all submissions but will contact if interested Toolroom Radio frequently features tracks from Toolroom Records releases, so getting a track on the label is the primary route to radio play. For PR, contact charlie@toolroomrecords.com. Guest mix slots not publicly advertised.', 'Global podcast; Apple Podcasts, Spotify; Mixcloud archive; 775+ episodes as of 2025', 'Toolroom Radio (presented by Mark Knight) is one of the most respected weekly tech house/house radio shows, broadcast globally with guest mix slots. Submitting demos to Toolroom Records via their online portal is the official route to getting tracks featured on the show.', '{"toolroomrecords.com/radio","toolroomrecords.com/demos"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Cr2 Live & Direct Radio Show', 'radio', 'free', 'web / SoundCloud / podcast / 70+ FM stations', '{"house","tech house","techno"}', 'email', 'https://cr2records.com/contact/', 'Contact via Cr2 Records general contact page. Include streaming link, release info, and artist bio. Original house/tech house tracks suitable for a global radio audience No dedicated promo submission email found on official pages. Contact via cr2records.com/contact/ or reach the production team at theboyinthecorner.co.uk. Approach is via the label/production team. Sample Tools by Cr2 (sampletoolsbycr2.com/opportunities/demo-submission/) also accepts demo submissions tied to the wider Cr2 ecosystem.', '18M+ weekly listeners; 70+ FM stations; 50+ countries; SoundCloud/podcast', 'Mark Brown''s Cr2 Live & Direct show reaches 18M+ weekly listeners across 70+ stations in 50+ countries — one of the most syndicated house radio shows globally. Promos submitted and featured here get extraordinary reach for an unknown.', '{"cr2records.com/radio","cr2records.com/contact"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Kaluki Radio', 'radio', 'free', 'podcast (Apple Podcasts) / SoundCloud', '{"tech house","house","techno"}', 'email', 'info@kaluki.co.uk', 'Include a SoundCloud or streaming link to your track or mix. Keep the pitch concise — who you are, what you''re sending. Original tech house/house productions Kaluki released music in 2026 (confirmed active). Radio show available on Apple Podcasts. This is a label contact that doubles as a route to radio feature.', 'Dedicated tech house fanbase; Apple Podcasts; global streaming; Ibiza presence', 'Kaluki is a Manchester-based independent tech house label and events brand (est. 2006) whose weekly radio podcast is an established community touchpoint. Reaching the label via info@kaluki.co.uk is a direct line to label boss Pirate Copy, who runs the show.', '{"kaluki.co.uk","podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/kaluki-radio/id1436583791"}', 'medium', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Glitterbox Radio', 'radio', 'free', 'web / Mixcloud / podcast', '{"house","disco house","soulful house","classic house"}', 'portal', 'https://www.labelradar.com/labels/glitterbox/portal', 'Submit via LabelRadar at labelradar.com/labels/glitterbox/portal. Streaming link with download option. Brief bio and social links. Track should fit Glitterbox''s disco/house/soulful aesthetic Glitterbox is a Defected sub-label; submissions via LabelRadar are reviewed by the wider Defected A&R team. Active as of 2025 (show episode 450 confirmed, BBC Radio 1 Dance x Glitterbox collaboration in June 2025).', 'Defected network audience; Mixcloud/SoundCloud; BBC Radio 1 Dance collaborations; global reach', 'Glitterbox Radio (run by Simon Dunmore / Defected sub-brand) is a weekly show celebrating the best in house, disco and dance music, broadcast globally. Submitting via the Defected/LabelRadar portal is the documented route for getting tracks considered for Glitterbox Radio airplay.', '{"labelradar.com/labels/glitterbox/portal","defected.com/glitterbox","ibiza-spotlight.com/magazine/2025/06/glitterbox-and-bbc-radio-1-dance-x-reel-house-music-legends-30th-anniversary"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('Selected.', 'youtube', 'free', 'YouTube / SoundCloud / Spotify', '{"house","deep house","melodic house"}', 'form', 'inbox@selectedbase.com', 'Streamable links only (SoundCloud, YouTube, Dropbox, Google Drive). Unreleased tracks preferred. Do not chase for a response Both the web form and email inbox@selectedbase.com are listed officially on selectedbase.com/submit', 'Multiple millions of YouTube plays; large SoundCloud following', 'Berlin-founded music blog and label with millions of YouTube views; curates high-quality house tracks for an engaged electronic audience and accepts demos directly from unknowns via its submit page.', '{"selectedbase.com/submit","youtube.com/channel/UCFZ75Bg73NJnJgmeUX9l62g"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('MrRevillz', 'youtube', 'paid', 'YouTube / SoundCloud / Spotify', '{"house","deep house","dance","electronic"}', 'portal', 'info@MrRevillz.com', 'Submit via the portal (not email for tracks). Receive email updates on verdict. House, dance, and electronic genres Dedicated portal at music.mrrevillz.com/Submissions is the primary channel; info@MrRevillz.com is for business inquiries only', '3M+ YouTube subscribers; 2B+ total views', 'One of the most established house/dance YouTube channels with 3M+ subscribers and 2B+ total views; runs a dedicated submission portal with feedback to all submitters — very accessible for unknowns.', '{"music.mrrevillz.com/Submissions","submithub.com/blog/mrrevillz","youtube.com/channel/UCd3TI79UTgYvVEq5lTnJ4uQ"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('House Nation', 'youtube', 'free', 'YouTube / SoundCloud', '{"house","tech house","deep house"}', 'portal', 'dylan@nations.io', 'Submit via LabelRadar portal. House, tech house, and adjacent electronic genres LabelRadar is the official submission portal. Contact email dylan@nations.io also cited (secondary source). isac.jivhed@nations.io also referenced.', '~3.92M YouTube subscribers; 1B+ total views', 'Premier YouTube destination for cutting-edge house music with ~3.9M subscribers and daily uploads; accepts music submissions via LabelRadar portal — one of the clearest open submission routes for independent house producers.', '{"labelradar.com/labels/housenation/profile","youtube.com/channel/UCj_Y-xJ2DRDGP4ilfzplCOQ","youtube.fandom.com/wiki/House_Nation"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('The Vibe Guide', 'youtube', 'free', 'YouTube / SoundCloud', '{"house","deep house","indie dance","nu disco","electronic"}', 'portal', 'tvgsubmissions@gmail.com', 'House, electronic, indie dance, nu disco, downtempo genres. Submit via portal or email Primary portal: submit.thevibeguide.net (returned 503 at time of fetch — may be temporarily unavailable); backup email tvgsubmissions@gmail.com confirmed via thevibeguide.net/contact and multiple secondary sources', 'Large established YouTube audience; active since 2012', 'One of the leading music curators on YouTube since 2012 with a multi-genre scope including house; maintains an open submission portal and email specifically for track submissions by artists at any level.', '{"thevibeguide.net/contact","submit.thevibeguide.net","submithub.com/blog/the-vibe-guide"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

  ('La Belle Musique', 'youtube', 'paid', 'YouTube / SoundCloud / Spotify / Twitch', '{"house","deep house","chill house","melodic"}', 'portal', 'rubin@labellemusique.co', 'Submit via Groover (fee-based per submission). Beautiful, chill, soulful house vibes preferred. Curators are described as ''very selective'' Groover is the official submission route; rubin@labellemusique.co is a promo contact cited by multiple secondary sources. Groover fees apply per submission.', 'Millions of YouTube views; active on SoundCloud and Spotify', 'Active since 2013, creates visually immersive house music compilations with large YouTube and SoundCloud audiences; accepts track submissions via Groover (paid, transparent) with a direct promo email as a fallback.', '{"groover.co/en/influencer/profile/0.la-belle-musique","youtube.com/channel/UCXKr4vbqJkg4cXmdvaAEjYw","submithub.com/blog/la-belle-musique"}', 'high', '2026-06-01'),

